\id 2SA Kyaka Enga Shorter Bible, SF codes August 20, 93
\h 2 SAMYUELE
\toc1 2 SAMYUELE
\toc2 2 Samyuele
\toc3 2 Sam
\mt1 2 SAMYUELE
\ip 1 Samyuele buku dokona arome pii wambo pyasi palamo. Dokome lao yaki nyiyamo dokona kimbu sepala 2 Samyuele dokona letamo. 2 Samyuele dokona akali Dapiti lenge baa kiŋi akali ingyuo wambu iso kareya yulu dokona lao pyasi palamo. Rombo 1 lao pao rombo 4 dokona Dapitimi yuu pakirename Juta lenge dokona iso kareya. Rombo 5 lao pao rombo 24 dokona Dapitimi Isaraele wambu peparae yuu Juta wambu dupwape yuu Isaraele lenge wambu dupwape peparae isiya. Dapitimi banya isingi yuu malu ingyuo nyelana pyuo karo banya gapomane doko porainyi pyambuyamo dokona arome pii dakena pyasi palamo. Pii yaka lao dokopa Dapiti baame poraiyuo Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao banya mona Anatu keta pyamalyapala kareyamo doko kandelyamano. Isaraele wambu dupwa rae maiyuo banya pii leyamuli pyuo kimbu moko minyuo pyuo kareyami. Dapiti dopa pyuo rolae pyuo kareyamopape yuu lapo dokopa nyipuli nyipuli lao suu pyao wambu dupwa keta randa maiyuo pyuo kareya. Dopa pyuo karapala baame yulu koo andake lapo piya. Anatunya poropeta akali Netane lenge dokome Dapiti banya koo dokona lao polo lamaiyamo dokopa Dapitimi elyame kumapala Anatu polo lamaiya. Anatumi Dapiti randa maiyamo dokopa Dapiti mee mumu laa nao randa nyuo kareya.
\ip Dapiti baa yulu andake pyuo akali mupwa ingyuo kareyamo dokome enakana Isaraele wambu dupwa moŋo nyepalape dokopa nakamana rora ambasu Dapiti kame see nao kiŋi akali Dapiti yale mendeme Dapitinya panda nyipyali lao suu pyao kareyami. Dopa lao suu pyao Dapitinya ikinyingi mendeme namwana kiŋinya panda doko nyakara, leyami.
\c 1
\s1 Sole Kumapeyamo Doko Dapiti Siya
\p 
\v 1 Sole kumapeyamopa Dapiti Amaleke wambu pipya yanda pyuo anamasi minyuo isa palyapala baa epo yuu Sikilake dokona yuu gii lama kareya.
\v 2 Dokopa yangama yulu repo dokona wane parange mende Solena komau anda pyuo paleyamo dokona piso epeya. Dokome banya kondange renge doko lasaka pilyuŋu lao dokopa banya komau dupwa minyuo kanguo dee banya kyawa awai pyao pipala Dapiti peteya dokona papala baa yuu dokona pangu soo piya.
\v 3 Dokopa Dapitimi akali doko piso soo lao, Emba anja karo epane? leya.
\p Leyamo dokopa akali dokome isingi lao, Namba Isaraele wambu komau anda pyuo palimi dokona namba iki kyawa lete nyuo epelyo, leya.
\p 
\v 4 Dokopa Dapitimi lao, Doo pipyamo dupwa apa pipyape namba langi, leya.
\p Namwana yanda singi dupwa pyakao pumisa namwana akali dupwa pyao kumako otami. Dee Solepa banya ikinyingi Jonatanepa opetaeko pyao kumakami, leya.
\p 
\v 5 Dokopa Dapitimi piso soo lao, Emba Sole Jonatanepa kumambi lao apa pipala silisi? leya.
\p 
\v 6 Dokopa akali dokome isingi lao, Namba yuu kyau Gilipoa dokona karapala kandapu dokopa Sole banya kaku dokome yuu dokona pii pyaro baa roya karapya. Dokopa mena oseme ipyuo penge uliuli dupwana yanda pela piso penge akali dupwape dee mena ose matana piso yanda pela penge dupwamepe baa repe kura lapala pyalena piyami.
\v 7 Dokopa baame kapu kyepala namba kandapala kee leya. Nambame isingi lao, Yaa, leyo.
\v 8 Dokopa baame namba apipi lao piso siya. Piso siyamosa cambame baa lamaiyuo, Namba Amaleke akali, leyo.
\v 9 Leyono dokopa Soleme lao, Nakamame namba pyaminyi dokome randa andake nyuo koo keta palyuo repeta kumaro ingilyamo dokona emba dae epapala namba pyao kumaka, leya.
\v 10 Leyamo dokopa baa pao palipala kumwara doko namba soo oteyo dokona namba baa pyao kumakala peyo. Dopa pipala kiŋinya kyawa rarange pee pingi dokope dee kinginya pisingi bange dokope nyepala emba minyuo jela epelyo, leya.
\p 
\v 11 Leyamo pii dupwa sepala Dapitimi baa kondome kumuo mona randapala banya komau dupwa minyuo pilyiya dee banya akali dupwa opetae dopako piyami.
\v 12 Dopa pipala nakama Sole dee Jonatanepa dee Isaraele rara Kamongona wambu malu yanda dokona kumuyaminyi dokona mona rando kumanda piso nenge naa nao pao alemanji ingiyami.
\p 
\v 13 Dokopa Dapitimi akali parange wai pii minyuo epeyamo doko pcco soo lao, Emba yuu anja rangese? leya.
\p Leyamopa akali dokome isingi lao, Namba Amaleke rara dokonaŋa. Namba nakamana yuu dakena palyuo karenge, leya.
\p 
\v 14 Dokopa Dapitimi baa piso soo lao, Doko dee apa pipyasa paka nao Kamongona rombo palyuo nyisi kiŋi doko pyao kumakamipisi? leya.
\v 15 Dapitimi banya akali dupwana mende kee lao nyepala, Baa pyao kumakana leya. Dokopa akali dokome Amaleke range doko waiya lao minyarapala baa pyao kumakaya.
\v 16 Dokopa Dapitimi Amaleke kumasi siyamo doko kando lao, Emba rangena kopetame pipi dokona emba kumulini. Kamongo dokome kiŋi karena lao rombo palyiyamo doko embame pyao kumakapu lapi kandape dokona emba range kumulini kande leya.
\s1 Sole Jonatanepana Lao Dapitimi Kondome Kumuo Ee Lao Kenane Piya
\p 
\v 17 Dapitimi kondome kumuo kenane dake Sole dee banya ikinyingi Jonatanepana suu pyao piya.
\v 18 Dee kenane doko Juta wambu dupwa peparae mana lamainya lao lamaiya. Kenane doko Akali Rolae Pingi Dupwana Buku dokona pyasi palamo.
\q1 
\v 19 Isaraele wambunya yuu kyau dupwana namwana lita akali dupwa kumami.
\q1 Dee namwana ami yanda singi akali porai paka nange dupwa isa palimi.
\q1 
\v 20 Dopa pipya lao yuu Gati dokonape dee yuu taone Asekelone kata barete dupwanape arome pyao laa nalapape.
\q1 Dee Pilisitia enda dupwa rae mainyi pyambwa nalapape.
\q1 Dee anatu lao suu pyaa nange wambu dupwana wanenge dupwa rae mainya laa nalapape.
\b
\q1 
\v 21 Yuu kyau Gilipoa dokona namwana yanda singi paka nange porai dupwa kumuyami dupwana konambe dupwa mee silyamo.
\q1 Dee Solena konambe mamba dokome kisapa naminyi mee silyamo.
\q1 Renge dokona apu pipyaepe dupwa yuu Gilipoa kyau dupwana pisa nana dee yuu dokona nenge pulya nana.
\q1 
\v 22 Jonatanena yanda dokome wambu malu piya.
\q1 Dee Sole baame wambu sakame kuma nao
\q1 banya wua gela dokome wambu porai dupwa pyao yanda pimwai dupwa pyao kumako piya.
\b
\q1 
\v 23 Wambu peparaeme Sole Jonatanepa kando rae maingi.
\q1 Nakamba laparae akali keyange.
\q1 Nakamba yuu gii peparae lete karo dokopa range puu minyuo karenge.
\q1 Dee nakamba laparae kapa kapa kumambi.
\q1 Nakambame mena laene poraipi dee yaka kambe puu lao makando pengenye dupwa isa palyuo nakamba kamame wakase makandapala nakambana nyisu petenge dupwa pingi.
\b
\q1 
\v 24 Isaraele enda dupwa, Solena lao kumanda pisipwape.
\q1 Baame nakama komau kone keyange kana malu penge dupwa nyuo jingi.
\q1 Dee kana goleme wasisi bange dupwame nakama kalya pyakange.
\b
\q1 
\v 25 Yanda singi porai paka nange dupwa isa palimi.
\q1 Nakamba yanda piyami dokona pyao kumuyami.
\q1 Yuu kyau dupwana Jonatane kumasi silyamo.
\b
\q1 
\v 26 Nambana yangone Jonatane nambame emba range ingi rando kondalyo. Nambame emba mona wakasa reto pingi dee embame namba mona kulisa wakasa retenge.
\q1 Akalimi enda mona retenge dokope daa kamame wakasa ingyuo nambwa mona retenge.
\b
\q1 
\v 27 Yanda singi porai paka nange dupwa yanda dokona isa palyuo oteyami.
\q1 Dee yanda pingi bange dupwa kwaeyo mee bange ingyuo peya.
\c 2
\s1 Dapiti Baa Juta Wambunya Kiŋi Ingiya
\p 
\v 1 Dokopa enakana Dapitimi Kamongo piso soo lao, Nambame yuu Juta taone dokona mende iso karala paowase? leya. Dokopa Kamongo dokome isingi lao, Kapa, leya.
\p Dapitimi kamba piso soo, Yuu taone angi anjukunya pao kararose? leya.
\p Dokopa Kamongo dokome isingi lao, Emba yuu Eperone dokona palyuo karala pena leya.
\v 2 Leyamosa Dapitimi banya etenge lama dolapo nyepala lanyuo yuu Eperone dokona peya. Enda mende Ainoame lenge yuu Jeserele range dee mende Apikale lenge yuu Kamele range akali Napalena enda waiya.
\v 3 Pao dokopa banya akalipi nakamana ree palupi dupwa minyuo pao yuu Eperone dokonape dee taone repeta singi dupwanape paleyami.
\v 4 Dokopa Juta akali dupwa yuu Eperone epapala Dapiti Juta wambunya kiŋi karena lao rombo palyiyami. Dopa piyami dokopa Dapitimi Jepese wambu yuu Giliate range dupwame Sole baa malu pilyaminyi leyami doko siya.
\v 5 Sepala baa akali lapo wai pii minyuo pena lao nembeya. Nembo lao, Nakamana kiŋi Sole baa ketae nembo rape rape letamano lao banya mondo lao malu piyami dokona Kamongo dokome nakama elyape keta pisinya.
\v 6 Kamongo dokome nakama anjiki pyuo iso karo yaki nyii nana. Nakamame Sole kando keyange piyami dokona nambame opetae nakama kando anjiki pyuo nyiso kararo, leya.
\v 7 Dokona nakamana kiŋi Sole doko kumuya. Dokopa Juta wambu dupwame namba nakamana kiŋi karare lao rombo palyiyami. Dokona nakama bange mende paka napala kandokondali pyuo porai ingyuo karalapape.
\s3 2:8—4:12 Akali Apena baame Solena ami dokona mupwa ingyuo kareya. Dopa pyuo karo baame Solena ikinyingi kingi Isiposete lenge baame rara yuu dulurena kareyaminyi dupwana kiŋi ingyuo iso karena leya. Leyamo dokopa yuu dulurena rara wambu dupwa yuu donorena rara wambu dupwa pipya yanda piyami. Yanda pyuo kareyaminyi dokopa nakamame Apenapa Isiposetepa pyao kumakayami. Dokopa Dapiti baa Isaraele wambupi Juta wambupi dupwa peparaena kiŋi ingyuo kareya.
\c 5
\s1 Dapiti Baa Isaraele Dee Juta Wambunya Kiŋi Ingyuo Kareya
\p 
\v 1 Enakana Isaraele rara dupwa peparae Dapiti baa yuu Eperone dokona kareya dokopa epeyami. Epapala baa lamaiyuo lao, Namwa embena rangena yongo ranjamape dokona leyami.
\v 2 Yuu wamba dokopa Sole baa namwana kiŋi kareya dokopa embame Isaraele wambu dupwa yanda piyami dokona laminyuo pee. Kamongo dokome emba kando lalu lao lao, Embame banya wambu dupwa rapu pyakamyuo dee emba nakamana kiŋi ingyuo karo piri, leya.
\v 3 Dokopa Isaraele akali mupwa dupwa peparae kiŋi Dapiti kareya dokona yuu Eperone epeyami. Dokopa baame Kamongona lenge kambu dokona nakama kando kana minyuo lalu lao leyamopa nakamame banya kyawa doko wele dokome kisakamiyaminyipa baa Isaraele wambu dupwana kiŋi ingiya.
\v 4 Dapiti baa ee kana akalisa rema ingyuo ando kareyamopa baa kiŋi ingiya. Dee baa kiŋi yulu pyuo kareyamo pao ee kana akalisa kisima ingiya.
\v 5 Dopa pyuo dee baa yuu Eperone dokona Juta peparae iso kareyamopa ee kana yanda ipingi dee kanya ingyuo peya. Dee yuu Jerusaleme dokona Isaraele wambupi Juta wambupi peparae pyuo iso karo piyamo pao ee kana akalisa rema dee ipisu rema peya.
\p 
\v 6 Kiŋi Dapitimi banya akali dupwa pipya yuu taone Jerusaleme doko pyao nyela parami yuu gii doko pyaka siya. Yuu taone dokona Jepusi rara dupwa palenge dupwame Dapiti baame kapa pyuo yuu taone doko pyao wini pyuo nyii nara lao suu piyami. Dokona lao nakamame Dapiti lamaiyuo lao, Nakama yuu dakena epa nalu narami. Dee kamame wambu lenge koope kimbu kwaengepe dupwame kata rokwarami ingilyamo, leyami.
\v 7 (Dopa leyaminyipape Dapiti baame nakamana yuu taone kame porai awali lao pisi kareyamo doko kingi Sayone lenge pyapala nyiyami. Nyepala nakamame kingi alowa pyuo Dapitinya taone, leyami.)
\p 
\v 8 Yuu gii dokopa Dapitimi banya akali dupwa lamaiyuo lao, Jepusi wambu dupwa namba epe kanda nange. Nakama dupwana mendeme Jepusi wambu dupwa epe kanda napala pyao kumakalana laoko karamisi? Nakamame dopa lao suu pyarami ramo dupwame suu ipyalukyana dokona kolo papala lenge koope kimbu kwaengepe dupwa peparae pyao kumakarami. (Renge dokona lao wambu kimbu koope lenge kwaengepe dupwa Kamongona anda dokona kolando epa narami, lenge.)
\p 
\v 9 Yuu taone kame porai awali lao pisi doko nyepala Dapiti dokona palipala yuu doko kingi Dapitinya taone, leya. Lapala baame yuu kyau kuki neta pyakaenge dorena yuu kyuwa ingiyasa yuu kyaso pambu karo simbuo ketae nyiyami dokona taone doko kanda soo piya.
\v 10 Kamongo Anatu Porai Wakasa doko baapa role kareyamosa Dapiti baa yuu gii peparae porainya renge paleyamopa ando porai ingyuo kareya.
\p 
\v 11 Yuu Taya dokona kiŋi akali Airame lenge kareyamo dokome Dapiti baa wai pii lamaiyuo isa kingi sita lenge dupwa peeyo dee kamonda akali anda pingi dupwape dee kana semene minyuo anda pingi akali dupwape peparae kiŋi Dapitinya anda kameya mende pyakaminya lao peeya.
\v 12 Dapitimi dopa piyamo doko kandapala dokopa Kamongo dokome namba Isaraele wambunya kiŋi angi karare lao rombo palyapyalyamo lao suu piya. Kamongo dokome banya wambu dupwa nyisalana suu pyao Isaraele yuu doko au pyuo palyiya.
\p 
\v 13 Dapiti baa yuu Eperone piso Jerusaleme pao dokopa kamba enda nyuo dee enda lapo konda pyuo nyuo piyamo dupwame yuu Jerusaleme dokona wane wanakepe mandeyami.
\v 14 Wane ane dupwana kingi dupwa dapa pyuo lao, Samua Sopape Netane Solomone,
\v 15 Ipya Elisua Nepeke Japiya,
\v 16 Elisama Eliyata Elipelete, leya.
\s1 Dapitimi Pilisitia Wambu Dupwa Pyapala Wini Piya
\p 
\v 17 Dapiti baa Isaraele wambunya kiŋi rombo palyami leyaminyi doko Pilisitia wambu dupwa siyami. Sepala nakamame baa pyalana minyarapala nyinya piyami. Doo leyaminyi doko anda porai mendena yalu pela peya.
\v 18 Dokopa Pilisitia wambu dupwa yuu pau lama lama Orepaime lenge dokona papala paleyami.
\v 19 Dokopa Dapitimi Kamongo doko piso soo lao, Nambame Pilisitia wambu dupwa pyaowape panda kaewase? Dee namwame pyala parama ramo doko embame namwa nyisarenepa pyao anamasi minyuo wini piramape mee lao piso siya.
\p Nambame emba porainya renge joo nyisaroŋo kapa pyala pena, leya.
\v 20 Dokona lao Dapiti yuu Bealo Perasimi dokona papala Pilisitia wambu pyao anamasi minyiya. Minyapala baame lao, Ipwa mee wau kanya palenge dopale ingyuo Kamongo dokome nambana nyisu petenge dupwa mee kanya kulimbwanyi peyakapya, leya. Renge dokona lao yuu kingi doko Bealo Perasimi lenge. Bealo Perasimi doko Kamongo dokome mee kanya kulimbwanyi peyapya dopale lenge.
\v 21 Pilisitia wambu dupwa pyakao ralo peyaminyi dokopa nakamana mee bange anatu lenge kingimi wasisi dupwa yaki nyepala peyami. Dupwa Dapitimi banya akali dupwa pipya nyuo soo peyami.
\p 
\v 22 Enakana Pilisitia wambu dupwa yuu pau lama Orepaime dokonako kamba papala palyuo kareyami.
\v 23 Dokopa namwame apa piramase lao Dapitimi Kamongo piso siya. Dokopa Kamongo dokome isingi yano pyao lao, Nakamame dakena piso rolae pao pyaa nalapape. Doloma palaminyi dokona donorena isa balasame lenge karamo dokona yanda pirami dokona rapa rapa pyuo karalapape, leya.
\v 24 Dokopa ketae isa mungi dulunya wambu lapome kalyuo paraminyi kimbu gulu galu lele laramo siyami kande doko nakamame dolama pyala pupwape. Pilisitia yanda singi ami dupwa pyao isa palyuo anamasi minyarami lao nambame nakama laminyuo wambo paro dokona kapa pyala pupwape, leya.
\v 25 Dokopa Dapitimi Kamongome pinya leyamuli pyuo Isaraele dupwame yuu taone Gepa piso Pilisitia dupwa pyao ralyuo pao yuu taone Gesa lenge dokona suu leyami.
\c 6
\s1 Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii // Palenge Bokote Doko Minyuo // Jerusaleme Epeyami
\p 
\v 1 Dapiti dee kamba mendepa Isaraele yanda singi dupwana akali yanda soo oto pingi dupwa yeelyo nyuo pao akali taosande akalisa rema (30,000) nyiya.
\v 2 Doko pipala Dapitimi akali dusipa lanyuo yuu taone Bala lenge yuu Juta dokona singi dokona Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko nyela peyami. Nakamame bokote doko Kamongo Porai Wakasa dokona lenge. Bokote ketae dokona aŋala yale wasisi lama karenge. Dokopa Kamongona petenge isa doko aŋala dolapona ketaerena singi.
\v 3 Akali Apinatapena anda yuu kyau dokona karenge dokona siyamo nyepala epo uliuli mena oseme ipyuo minyuo penge enenge dokona reteyami. Dokopa akali Usa Aiyopa Apinatapena ikinyingi dolapo uliuli doko minyuo peyambi.
\v 4 Aiyo dokome uliuli ipyuo peyamo dokona wambako peya.
\v 5 Dokopa uliuli ipyuo peyamo dokona Dapitimoo dee Isaraele wambu peparaepe rae maiyuo kenane andake pyao pyakalyuo pyao Anatunya kingi ketae pyambuo peyami. Dopa pyuo nakamame rambyalu lao kurulu lao lakuli pyao isa lomasi doo doo lao gita pyao peyami.
\p 
\v 6 Pao akali Nakonena yuu nenge witi pyao injingi mare dokona epeyami. Dokona mena bulamakao yale kingi okose lenge dolapo lukumapala pao palinya piyambisa akali Usa baame kingi pyambwapala Anatunya Kana Minyuo Lalu Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko minyareya.
\v 7 Doko Usame Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko angi mende daaŋa lao suu pyao minyandeyasa dokopako aopa Kamongo dokome imbwuapala baa pyao kumuya. Dopa piyasa Usa baa yuu dokona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote siyamo dokona repeta kumuya.
\v 8 Dokona yuu doko kingi Perese Usa lenge. Renge doko Kamongome Usa randa maiya lao lenge. Kamongo dokome imbu singi nyepala Usa baa randa maiyasa Dapiti baa ama wakasa imbwaya.
\p 
\v 9 Enakana Dapiti baame Kamongo doko kando pakapala lao, Epapu apa pyuo nambame Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko nyuo minyuo parose? leya.
\v 10 Lapala Dapiti bokote doko nyuo minyuo banya yuu taone Jerusaleme dokona paa naro, leya. Baame Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko nyepala Jerusaleme kata penge doko yaki nyepala yuu taone Gati range akali Opetitome lenge dokona anda lanyuo peya.
\v 11 Akali Opetitomena anda dokona Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko siyamo pao kana rema ingiya. Dopa piyamo dokopa Kamongome Opetitome baape banya ree palu dupwape elyape keta pisinyi pyambuya.
\p 
\v 12 Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko akali Opetitomena anda siya dokome Opetitome baape banya ree palu dupwape dee banya bange dupwanape Kamongome elyape keta pisilyamo leyami doko Dapitimi siya. Dokona lao Dapitimi Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko akali Opetitomena anda siyamo doko nyuo minyuo Jerusaleme panya wambu peparae rae wakasa maiyami.
\v 13 Dokopa akali dupwame bokote doko soo kata nyuo peyami. Pao yuu kuki lama kata nyuo papeyaminyi dokopa Dapitimi karena, leya. Lapala Dapitimi Kamongo doko mena bulamakao kali mendepa dee mena bulamakao yakane rondo lasi mendepa pyao kiso maiya.
\v 14 Dapiti baa komau ama keyange mende bole bale lao wapupala banya porai renge peparaeme Kamongo lakando kenane pyao rae maiyuo wamya lyuo kareya.
\v 15 Dopa pyuo Dapiti baape Isaraele wambu peparaepe pii poraiyuo lao rae maiyuo bikuli pii poo lao Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko nyuo minyuo Jerusaleme peyami.
\p 
\v 16 Yuu taone dokona bokote doko minyuo sukusa dokona peyami dokopa kiŋi Dapiti baa rae maiyuo wamya lyuo malya pyao Anatunya kingi ketae pyambuo peya. Dokopa Solena wanenge Maikele lenge dokome Dapiti doo piyamo doko windowa kata kandapala epe kando awa naya.
\v 17 Nakamame bokote doko minyuo papala Dapitimi kapa seraŋa lao komau anda piyamo dokona reteyami. Retapala enakana baame mena pyao kiso dee Kamongopa nakamape malu palyuo yalya kando piso maiyuo piyami.
\v 18 Dopa pyuo baame mena pyao kiso maiyuo otapala dokopa baame Kamongona kingi lao wambu dupwa elyape keta pisiya.
\v 19 Dopa pipala Dapitimi wambu peparae nenge mokwa soo maiya. Baame Isaraele enda akalipi dupwa mendaki mendaki lao nenge borete mendaki larapu maiyuo mena minju isarena kisasi mendaki lao maiyuo dee isa girapo jingi yando dupwa maiyuo piya. Dokopa wambu peparae anda peyami.
\p 
\v 20 Dokopa enakana Dapiti baa banya ree palu dupwa yako lao anda peya. Dokopa enda Maikele doko baa Dapiti kandala epeya. Epapala lao, Isaraele wambunya kiŋi doko, epapu baa range kingi ketae nembo karo ipwamo, leya. Banya akali mupwa dupwana kendemande wanake dupwana lenge kambu dokona elya pali nao pyaloko lalya lana pyuo kopyali ingyuo karalamo, leya.
\p 
\v 21 Dokopa Dapitimi isingi lao, Namba doo pipunu dupwa Kamongona kingi ketae nembo pipu. Embena rakanepe dee embena ree palupi dupwana panda nyuo namba banya Isaraele wambu peparaena kiŋi ingyuo rombo palyiya. Dokona namba rae maiyuo wamya lyuo pyakalyuo pyao Kamongona kingi ketae nembo ene pyuoko paro ingilyamo.
\v 22 Dopa pyuo namba kamame elya renge nyeronopa namba kamame isa paronopape embame namba mende daaŋa lao suu pyarenepape wanake doo letene dusipame namba mee mende ulipilinyi lao suu pyarami, leya.
\p 
\v 23 Maikele Solena wanenge doko wane wanakepe mende manja nao mee petenge.
\c 7
\s1 Netaneme Wai Pii Dapiti Lamaiya
\p 
\v 1 Kiŋi Dapiti banya anda dokona kapa palu pisipiyamo dokopa Kamongo dokome banya nyisu petenge dupwame pyasasaramiŋi lapala nyiso kyawa lete nyiya.
\v 2 Dokopa kiŋi dokome poropeta akali Netane lamaiyuo lao, Namba dae isa sita lengeme anda pisi dokona palo. Dopa pipunupape Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko mee komau anda pisi dokona silyamo. Doko kapa daa, leya.
\p 
\v 3 Dokopa Netaneme isingi lao, Emba keta Kamongo doko karamo dokome embena suu pinginya pinya suu pilini dupwa pipi, leya.
\v 4 Leyamopape yuu gii kukwa dokopa Kamongome Netane dopa lamaiyuo lao,
\v 5 Nambana kendemande akali Dapiti doko kando nambame lalamo lao lamaila pupi. Embame ingyuo nambana tembole anda doko pyaka nare, lape.
\v 6 Nambame Isaraele wambu dupwa yuu Isipi piso kiiramo nyuo lanyuo epeyono yuu gii dokona piso pao dakepa nambana tembole anda mende pyaka nayami. Namba mee komau anda dokona iki palipapu papyuo kareyo.
\v 7 Namba Isaraele wambu dupwa pipya papyuo karapunu dupwana nambame akali mupwa rombo palyiyunu dupwa kando, Akipamo nakamame isa sita lenge dokome nambana tembole anda mende pyaka nalyamisi? lao piso see nalu nange.
\p 
\v 8 Dokona lao nambana kendemande Dapiti lamaipi, Namba Kamongo Porai Wakasa dokome emba mena sipisipi rapu pyuo kakopasa karenepa nyepala emba nambana Isaraele wambu dupwana kiŋi ingyuo karare lao rombo palyiyu kande.
\v 9 Nambame emba peene dupwa peparae role peyo. Dee nambame embena nyisu petenge dupwa nyuo isa palyakayo. Dee yuu muu dupwana akali mupwa porai lapo kingi ketae pupyamo karaminyi dopale ingyuo embena kingi andake ingyuo ketae nembakaro.
\v 10-11 Nambana Isaraele wambu dupwa nambame yuu mende rombo palyuo nyakamiyu dokona nakama au pyuo palyuo kararami. Dokopa nakama wambu koo mendemepe pyaope randa maiyuope pii nalu narami. Wamba kanda soo yuu dakena epo piso pao epapu karaminyi dokopape wambu koo dupwame nakama pyao randa maiyuo kareyami. Dopa piyaminyipape deeko dopa pii nara ingilyamo. Embena nyisu petenge dupwame pyasasaramiŋi lapala nambame emba kyawa lete nyuo dee embena rara dupwa jingi para pyao para lao lalu lao langilyu.
\v 12 Emba kumarene dokopa embena rora ambasu dupwa pipya role pyao malu pirami. Dokopa nambame embena ikinyi dokona mende kiŋi rombo palyaro. Dopa pirunupa banya kiŋi yulu doko porai ingyuo ando para.
\v 13 Doo kiŋi rombo palyuo kararono dokome nambana tembole anda pyakara. Dee nambame banya manjo paramo dupwanako akali dupwa kiŋi ingyarapu palyuo puu parami lao rombo palyarapu piru.
\v 14 Namba banya rakange ingyaro dee baa nambana ikinyingi ingyuo para. Baa koo piramo dokopa rakangeme banya ikinyingi pyalana pyuo randa mainginyili pyuo randa mairu.
\v 15 Dokona nambana mona reto alowa pii nange renge doko Sole keta nyisa nyiyu doko suu pyao baa keta nyisa nyii naro. Sole keta dopa piyunu doko emba banya panda nyuo kiŋi karalase lao piyu.
\v 16 Yuu peparae emba wane manjo jingi parape lao puu pare. Nambame embena kiŋi yulu doko sulu jinya lao piru. Dee nambame embena rara dokona akali dupwa iki embena panda nyuo kiŋi inginya lao rombo palyarapu pyuo puu paro, lapya, lamaipi, leya.
\p 
\v 17 Anatumi nolakao epo lamaiyamo dupwa peparae Netaneme Dapiti lamaiya.
\s1 Dapitimi Anatu Ange Lao Ateŋa // Leya Doko
\p 
\v 18 Kiŋi Dapiti baa Kamongona komau anda dokona kolando pao banya lenge kambu dokona isa pisipala ateŋa lao lao, Kamongo Mupwa Andake Wakasa doko, embame wambo nambana lao yulu pipinyi dupwa nambape dee nambana ree palu dupwa yulu keyange pimwandena pipinde daa.
\v 19 Kamongo Mupwa Andake Wakasa doko, epapu embame kamame wakasako ingyuo pilini. Dee ee kana ene eparamo dupwana embame nambana para pyasi dupwa kando apa pyakare dupwana lao lalu lao lapi. Dokona embame namba lasaka pipi kandapi.
\v 20 Dokona nambame emba aki mende konda pyuo langiru. Namba embena kendemande akali embame soo gisilini.
\v 21 Doo yulu andake pipinyi dupwa embena yulu pinya suu pyapinyili pyuo pipi. Embame namba yulu andake pipinyi dupwa see, lao langipi.
\v 22 Emba ama ketaele, Kamongo Mupwa Andake Wakasa doko. Emba yale mendali kara nange. Namwame yuu peparae emba iki Anatu karenge lao soo nyilyamano.
\v 23 Isaraele wambu karapusi ingyuo kendemande yulu pyuo kareyaminyipa embena rangena wambu ingyuo kiiramo nyuo lanyuo epee kande. Yuu mupwa dupwa peparaena Isaraele rara dopale rara mende pali nange. Embame yulu andake keyange dupwa namwa keta pii dokome yuu muu dusipana embena kingi doko ketae pelyamo. Isaraele wambu Isipi piso emba rangena ingyuo manda rao nyingi dupwa nakama epo palena laro karo dokopa embame wambu rara wakale dupwape nakamana mee bange anatu lenge dupwape pyao nembee.
\v 24 Isaraele dupwa embame emba rangena wambu ingyuo puu parami lao rombo palyapala emba Kamongo doko namwana Anatu angingyuo karenge.
\p 
\v 25 Dokona epapu Kamongo Anatu, nambape nambana ree palu dupwape kando embame mende piru lao lalu lao lee kande doko pipi. Dee dopaleko yuu peparae pyuo karalu karape.
\v 26 Dokopa embena kingi doko ketae para. Dopa piramopa wambu dupwame laoko karo, Kamongo Porai Wakasa doko Isaraele peparae keta karamo, larami. Embame nambana rara dokona akali dupwa iki kiŋi ingyuo karena lao yuu gii peparae rombo palyarapu piri.
\v 27 Kamongo Porai Wakasa Isaraele wambunya Anatu. Embame yulu pyakarene dupwa peparae namba nolakao langyuo dee nambana rara dokona akali dupwa kiŋi ingyuo karena laro langii kande dokome namba paka nao emba kando ateŋa dake langilyu.
\p 
\v 28 Dokona epapu Kamongo Mupwa Andake Wakasa doko emba Anatu. Emba lalu lao lenge pii doko alowa pii nao minyuo karalu karenge. Lalu lao lenge pii keyange dake namba keta langii kande.
\v 29 Nambame nambana wambu dupwa elyape keta pisinyi dopaleko ingyuo pisakape lao emba piso silyu. Emba Kamongo Mupwa Andake Wakasa dokome dopa lao lalu lao leene dokome embena elyape pisingi renge doko nambana para pyasi dupwa keta palyuo puu para, leya.
\s3 8:1-18 Dapitimi yuu liti wakale range lapo Isaraele repeta kareyaminyi dupwa nyuo anamasi minyapala baa Isaraele dokona kiŋi angingyuo karo yuu peparaena iso kareya.
\c 9
\s1 Dapitimi Akali Mipiposeta Kando Keyange Piya
\p 
\v 1 Yuu mendepa Dapitimi piso soo lao, Akali Solena ree palu dokona wambu pyarepala peya mende karase? Mendali karara ramo doko Jonatanena reke lao nambame baa anjiki pyuo nyisalana, leya.
\p 
\v 2 Solena ree palu dupwana kendemande akali Sipa lenge doko kareya. Baa kee lapala kiŋi doko kandala pena leyami. Leyamisa baa kiŋi peteyamo dokona peya. Peyamo dokopa kiŋi dokome piso soo lao, Emba Sipase? leya.
\p Leyamo dokopa Waa. Namba embena kendemandeko, leya.
\p 
\v 3 Dokopa kiŋi dokome kambako piso soo, Nambame Kamongo Anatu kando lalu lao lao anjiki pyuo nyisaro leyo dokona kiŋi Solena ree palu dokona wambu lapo pyarepala pao karamisi? leya.
\p Dokopa Sipame isingi lao, Jonatanena ikinyingi mendeko iki pyarepala peyamo karamo doko baa kimbu kooŋo, leya.
\p 
\v 4 Dokopa kiŋi dokome piso soo, Baa anja karase? leya. Dokopa baame lao, Yuu Lotemba dokona akali Makya Amielena ikinyingi dokona anda karamo, leya.
\v 5 Leyasa kiŋi Dapitimi akali lapome baa nyela pena lamaiya.
\p 
\v 6 Jonatanena ikinyingi Solena kauwange akali Mipiposeta baa epeya. Epapala baame Dapiti angingyuo karamo lao suu pyao yuu dokona pangu siya. Dokopa Dapitimi baa yako lao kingi nyiya dokopa baa namba embena yulu pyakange akali doko, leya.
\p 
\v 7 Dapitimi isingi lao, Emba paka napipi. Embena rakane Jonatane doko nambame kame see nao suu pyao karo banya reke lao nambame emba anjiki pyuo nyisaro. Nambame embena kauwane Sole dokona yuu dupwa peparae emba range jero. Dee emba yuu peparae nambapa nenge role pyao nala epare, leya.
\p 
\v 8 Dokopa Mipiposeta baa kambako yuu dokona pangu sepala lao, Namba suwa kumasi dokona mendeke ingyuo peto doŋo akipamo embame namba kando ama keyange pilisi? leya.
\p 
\v 9 Dokopa kiŋi Dapitimi Solena kendemande akali Sipa doko epena lapala lamaiyuo lao, Nambame Solena yuu dupwape dee banya ree palu wambu dupwana bange peparaepe embena akali mupwa Sole dokona kauwange akali Mipiposeta doko mai, leya.
\v 10 Dokona embape embena wane dupwape dee kendemande akali dupwapeme embena akali mupwa Solena ree palu dupwana lao yuu dokona yulu pyuo nenge wara pyakamirami. Dopa pipala nenge wambu piramo dupwa minyuo epo Solena wambu ree palu dupwa mairami. Dopa piraminyipape Mipiposeta baa yuu peparae nambapa role pyao nenge nala epara, leya. Akali Sipa banya ikinyingi akalisa ipisu kingi paki (15) dee banya kendemande akali akalisa lama (20) karenge.
\p 
\v 11 Sipame isingi lao, Emba kiŋi andake dokome pipi letenele pyuo nambame peparae piru, leya.
\p Mipiposeta baa kiŋinya ikinyingi angiko ingyuo kiŋi role piso nenge neya.
\v 12 Mipiposeta banya ikinyingi parange mende Makya lenge. Akali Sipana ree palu dupwa peparae Mipiposetana kendemande ingyuo karo yulu pyakamiyami.
\v 13 Dokopa akali Mipiposeta kimbu laparae kwaeyasi doko yuu Jerusaleme paleya. Palipala baa kwuara yangara peparae lao kiŋi role pyao nenge nao kareya.
\s3 10:1-19 Dapitinya ami yanda singi dupwame Amone wambupi Siria wambupi pyao anamasi minyiyami.
\c 11
\s1 Dapiti Betesepapa
\p 
\v 1 Ee kana peparae lao kupwa pingi yuu gii doko otara ingiyamopa kiŋi peparae nakamana nyisu petenge dupwa pipya yanda pela parapu pingi. Dokopa Dapitimi banya akali mupwa dupwape dee Isaraele yanda singi dupwape akali Joapeme role pyao yanda pela pena lao nembeya. Dupwame papala Amone wambu dupwa pyao isa palyuo anamasi minyapala nakamame yuu taone Orapa doko nyiyami. Dopa piyaminyipa Dapiti baa Jerusaleme karo kaeya.
\p 
\v 2 Yuu gii mendepa alemanji kwualepalepa Dapiti baa luu palu soo lenge rapala kiŋinya anda ketae dokona pulyuo peya. Dokona pao karo kandeyamo dokopa enda mende wate pyuo kareyamo kandeya. Enda baa ama keyange wakasa mende kareya.
\v 3 Dokona enda baa apipi lao kando pyarako sela pena lao akali mende nembeya. Dokopa enda doko akali Elamena wanenge Betesepa lenge doko yuu Iti range akali Yurayana etenge lao lamaiyamo siya.
\v 4 Sepala Dapitimi wai pii minyingi akali dupwame enda doko nyela pena leya. Leyamopa akali dupwame papala enda doko nyuo minyuo epo maiyaminyipa baame ama mona wakasa retapala role pyao palu karo piya. Enda baa kamanda anda palipala mee ingiyamopa dee kapa peteya. Dokopa enda baa kapu kyuo anda peya.
\v 5 Dokopa enakana enda baa wane paleyasa baa dopa pilyamo lao Dapiti lamainya lao wai nembeya.
\p 
\v 6 Enakana Dapitimi akali Joape keta wai pii nembapala lao, Yuu Iti range akali Yuraya doko namba karo dokona pena lena leya. Dokona lao Joapeme akali Yuraya baa Dapiti keta pena leya.
\v 7 Leyamopa Yuraya baa epo pyaka sepeyamo dokopa Dapitimi baa piso soo, Joapemoo dee yanda singi dupwape kapa karamisi dee yanda angi pimi dupwa apa pyuo pimisi? leya.
\v 8 Lapala baame Yuraya kandoko lao, Anda imambu kuki sela pena leya. Dokopa Yuraya baa yaki nyuo peya. Peyamopa Dapitimi bange lapo baa mainya lao akali dupwame minyuo pena leya.
\v 9 Dopa pyuo pena leyamopape Yuraya baa anda paa napala kiŋi Dapitinya isingi akali dupwa pipya kiŋinya anda yuupi kame kambu kii mare dokona paleya.
\v 10 Doko Yuraya baa anda paa napya leyaminyi Dapitimi sepala baa piso soo lao, Emba yuu wambale anda yuupi yaki nyepala dee ipi kandape akipamo emba anda paa napisi? leya.
\p 
\v 11 Leyamo dokopa Yurayame isingi lao, Isaraele akali dupwape Juta akali dupwape yandana wakale karaminyipa Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko nakamame reto karaminyi. Dee nambana akali mupwa Joapemoo banya akali mupwa dupwa pipya yanda kamana pao komau anda pyuo palaminyiko. Dokona nambame apa pipala anda pao nenge ipwape nao dee nambana enda dokopa palu pirusi? Nambame kinyi kinyi lalu lao leto doko nambame yulu dopale dupwa pii naro leya.
\p 
\v 12 Dokopa Dapitimi lao, Kapaŋa. Yuu gii epapu peparae dae kararenepa rakya emba anda kapu kyuo puu lao nembaro, leya. Dokona lao akali Yuraya baa yuu gii doko karo dee yangama opetae Jerusaleme dokona karo piya.
\v 13 Dopa piyasa Dapitimi banya anda epena lapala nengepe ipwa biyape maiya. Maiyamopa Yuraya baa ipwa biya napala kyawa sisingi bolombalo leyasa yuu gii kukwa dokopa baa anda paa naya. Paa napala banya porangelye dokome yapu napala kiŋinya isingi akali dupwana palenge panda dokona pao paleya.
\p 
\v 14 Paleyamo yangama dokopa Dapitimi pepa mende pyapala Yurayame Joape maiyakana lao minyuo pena leya.
\v 15 Dokona baame dopa lao piya. Akali Yuraya dake yanda isare rao piyami kande dokopa lane mupwa dokona nenge nyuo palyape. Dopa pipala nyisu petenge dupwame baa pyao kumakanaleŋe nakama mee mendele lano pao karalapape, leya.
\v 16 Joape baamoo yanda singi dupwape yuu taone doko nyelana pyao pena karo dokopa Joape Yuraya baa yanda isare rao piyami dokona nengena pena leya.
\v 17 Dokopa nyisu petenge yanda singi Amone range dupwa yuu taone dokona nyisa epapala Joapena yanda singi dupwa pipya yanda piyami. Dokopa Dapitinya akali mupwa lapo pyao kumakayami dee Yuraya baa pyao kumakayamiko.
\p 
\v 18 Dokopa Joapeme yanda piyaminyi dupwana lao pii lapo Dapiti lamaiyuo nembeya.
\v 19 Baame pii angi minyuo paramo akali doko lamaikondali pyuo lao, Embame yanda pimwano dupwana lao lamaiparenepa
\v 20 mende baa imbwuapala emba piso soo lao, Akipamo nakamame yuu taone dokona ama repeta doloma pyala pumisi? Nakamana nyisu petenge dupwame kana kame dokona ketae karo walekyame pyarami doko see namisi?
\v 21 Akali Apimeleke Gitionena ikinyingi doko pyao kumakayami kande doko nakama suu pyaa namisi? Doko yuu Tepese dokonako enda mendeme kana kame dokona ketae karapala kana kameya mende malyapala pyao kumakaya kande. Dokona akipamo nakama kana kame dokona ama repeta pumisi? lao laralya kande. Dopa pyuo kiŋi dokome piso siya kande dokopa embame baa lamaiyuo, Embena akali mupwa Yuraya kandape doko opetae pyao kumakami lape leya, Joapeme.
\p 
\v 22 Dokona lao wai minyingi akali doko Dapiti peteya dokona papala Joapeme lena lao lamaiyamuli pyuo pii dupwa Dapiti lamaiya.
\v 23 Lamaipala lao, Namwana nyisu petenge dupwa porayapala yuu taone nyisa epo namwa pyala iminyipape namwame nakama pyao pao yuu taone kame kambu dokona pyambwamwa.
\v 24 Dokopa nakamame kana kame dokona ketae karapala walekya dupwame namwa piyami dokopa emba kiŋi andake dokona akali yanda singi mupwa lapo pyao kumakao dee embena akali mupwa Yuraya baa opetaeko pyao kumakayami, leya.
\p 
\v 25 Dokopa Dapitimi pii wai minyingi akali doko lamaiyuo lao, Embame Joape baa mona minyarambu lamaiyuo, Baa mona randa nana lape. Renge doko yanda dokona api kumara doko see nange kandale. Dokona embame baa lamaipala yanda kando porai ingyuo pipala Amone wambu dupwa pyao isa palyuo anamasi minyapala yuu taone doko pyao kokwa soo nembena lena leya.
\p 
\v 26 Dokopa enda Betesepame banya akalingi doko yandana kumulyamo leyaminyi doko sepala baa kumanda peteya.
\v 27 Dopa pyuo kumanda piso otapeyaminyi gii dokopa Dapitimi enda doko banya anda epena lao wai nembeya. Enda doko epo banya etenge ingyuo pisipala wane mende manjakamiya. Dopa piyamopape Kamongo dokome Dapitimi doo piyamo dokona rae mai naya.
\c 12
\s1 Netaneme Dapitinya Koo Dupwa // Polo Leya
\p 
\v 1 Kamongome poropeta akali Netane Dapiti kareya dokona pena leya, Netaneme Dapiti kareya dokona papala baa lamaiyuo lao, Akali lama yuu taone mendakinyako paleyambi. Doo paleyambi dokona mende akali kamongo dee mende akali pendewa.
\v 2 Akali kamongo doko mena bulamakaope sipisipipi dupwa malu minyiya.
\v 3 Dokopa akali pendewa dokome mena sipisipi ikyane inya mendaki iki ropo pyao nyepala minyiya. Baame mena doko au pyuo rapu piyasa banya anda dokona karo andapala banya wane wanakepe dupwa pipya role pyao kareyami. Dokopa banya nenge dupwana maiyuo pee kapo baa rangena dokona ipwa nena lao dee banya pai dupwana kupyaro piso piya. Dopa pipala mena sipisipi ikyane doko banya wanenge dopale ingiya.
\v 4 Yuu mendepa upunili wambu mende akali kamongo dokona anda epeya. Dokopa akali kamongo dokome banya mena rangena dokona mende nyepala upunili minyuo pyao kisakaminya lao suu pyaa naya. Dopa pipala akali pendewa dokona mena sipisipi ikyane doko nyepala pyao kiso akali doko nenge piya, leya. Netaneme Dapiti lamaiya. \fig Akali kamongo doko mena bulamakaope sipisipipi dupwa malu minyiya.|alt="two pictures combine together but used two captions" src="AV122a_122b" size="col" ref="12:2"\fig*\fig Akali pendewa dokome mena sipisipi ikyane inya mendaki iki ropo pyao nyepala minyiya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="12:3"\fig*
\p 
\v 5 Dokopa Dapitimi akali kamongo bange malu retenge doko kando ama wakasa imbwuapala lao, Namba Kamongo Lete Karenge doko kando lalu lao leto. Akali doo piyamo doko baa pyao kumapengeleŋe.
\v 6 Renge doko baa yulu kopetame piya dokona baame bange kisima larapu akali pendewa doko maira, leya.\fig Akali pendewa dokona mena sipisipi ikyane doko nyepala pyao kiso akali doko nenge piya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="12:4"\fig*
\p 
\v 7 Leyamo dokopa Netaneme lao, Emba akali dokoŋo, leya. Lapala lao, Kamongo Isaraele wambunya Anatu dokome dapa lapya. Nambame emba Sole keta kingi raka lao kiiramo nyepala Isaraele wambunya kiŋi wasiyu kande.
\v 8 Nambame banya kiŋi yulupi dee banya endape dupwa nyuo jiyu. Jepala Isaraele peparaepe dee Juta peparaepena emba kiŋi ingyuo nambame rombo palyiyu. Doko jiyunu dusipa kapa ingya napyali doko lama konda pyuo jipuli.
\v 9 Dokona lao akipamo embame nambana mawa pii dupwa warombo see nalese? Akipamo embame yulu koo dake piisi? Embame akali Yuraya nyepala yandana pyao kumakae. Embame Amone akali dupwame pyao kumakana lee. Lapala dokopa enakana banya etenge embame nyakamipi.
\v 10 Embame namba kando kamba lapala akali Yurayana etenge nyakami dokona epapu embena para pyao manjiraminyi dupwana yaka lao randa andake lapo nyuo pyao kumarapuko pyuo para.
\v 11 Nambame emba kando lalu lao leto, Doko emba range ree palu dokona mendeme emba keta randa nyuo jinya lao piru. Pipala nambame embena etene dupwa nyepala akali wakale mende mairunupa akali baame enda dupwa panembena kepo pyuo nyeramopa emba kandare.
\v 12 Renge doko emba koo yalu pyuo pii. Piinyipape nambame dake Isaraele wambu peparaeme kandena lao panembena pinya lao piru, lapya, leya.
\p 
\v 13 Dokopa Dapitimi lao, Namba Kamongopa ingyuo koo pipu, leya.
\p Netaneme isingi lao, Kamongo dokome nyuo kame sakaraŋa. Emba kuma nare.
\v 14 Dopa pirinyipape embame yulu koo dopale pyuo Kamongo angiŋi lao suu pyaa naene dokona embena wane Betesepame mandeyamo doko kumara, leya.
\v 15 Lapala Netane baa anda peya.
\s1 Dapitinya Ikinyingi Kumuya
\p Kamongome Yurayana etenge dokome Dapitinya wane manjakamiya doko anga pinya lao randa maiya.
\v 16 Dokopa Dapitimi Kamongo kando wane doko mee petena lao ateŋa leya. Dopa piyamopape Dapiti baa nenge wasaka pyuo yuu kukwa peparae banya luu palenge panda dokona papala rate ketae pali nao mee isa panda dokona palipapu piya.
\v 17 Banya anda dokona yulu pingi akali mupwa dupwame baa paleya dokona papala pyaleto nyuo roya pisimwali lao piyaminyipape baa simbi simbi pipala nakama pipya role pyao nenge mendepe naa naya.
\v 18 Dopa pyuo karo mende papeyamopa enakana wane doko kumuya. Dokopa Dapitinya akali mupwa dupwame dopa pyuo wane doko kumapya lao baa lamainya pakayami. Pakapala nakamame lao, Wane doko lenge rao peteyamo pii lamaiyama dokopa Dapitimi namwa pii langya naya kande. Banya wane doko kumapya lao apa pyuo namwame baa lamairamase? Mende dee baa range randa lapo nyisasara, leyami.
\p 
\v 19 Dokopa Dapitimi doloma mendeme mende kando isa isa pii leyami doko kandeya. Kandapala baame wane doko kumalamolyamo lao soo nyiya. Dopa pipala baame nakama piso soo lao, Wane doko kumapyase? leya.
\p Dokopa nakamame isingi lao, Waa, baa kumapya, leyami.
\p 
\v 20 Dokopa Dapiti banya panda dokona isa yuu dokona paleya doko sipurapala wate piya. Pipala banya kyawasi kome pipala komau alowa pyuo wakale wapuya. Enakana baa Kamongona anda papala Kamongo lakandeya. Dopa pyuo lakando piso banya anda papala nenge jinya lao piso sepala mokwa soo maiyapeyaminyi dokopa neya.
\v 21 Dopa piyasa banya akali mupwa dupwame emba doo pilini doko namwa soo gisa nalyamano, lao baa kando leyami. Wane doko lenge rao pisipyamo dokopa emba nenge naa nao ee lao pisipi. Dopa pyuo pisipinyipape baa kumapapya dokopa aopa emba sipurapala nenge nelene, leyami.
\p 
\v 22 Dapitimi isingi lao, Waa. Kinyi wane baa mee lenge rao peteyamo dokopa namba nenge wasaka pyuo ee lao peteyo. Renge doko Kamongome namba kondome kumuo nyisapala wane doko kumunya laka nara lao suu piyu.
\v 23 Dopa piyunupape epapu wane baa kumapya dokona namba akipamo nenge naa nao pisiru. Dopa piru dokome nambame wane doko lete dee nyerose? Yuu gii lapona namba baa pupyamo kata dokonako paro. Baa dee namba keta kapu kyuo epa nara, leya Dapitimi.
\s1 Solomone Mandeyambi
\p 
\v 24 Enakana Dapitimi banya etenge Betesepa mona minyarambu rapu piya. Dopa pyuo baa enda dokopa role paleyambi. Dokopa enda baa wane ane mandeya. Doko Dapitimi wane kingi Solomone leya. Kamongo dokome wane doko mona reteya.
\v 25 Retapala poropeta akali Netane lamaiyuo, Kamongome baa mona reteyamo dokome wane kingi Jetitaya lena leya. Kingi Jetitaya lenge doko Ipuru pii dokona Kamongome mona wakasa retenge lenge.
\s3 12:26—14:20 Yuu Amone dokona taone mupwa doko Dapitimi pyao nyiya. Dapitinya ree palu dokona pundu sipureya. Epesalomena yangonge mendeme Epesalomena pemalenge kingi Tama lenge kepo pyuo nyiyamosa Epesalome baame pyao kumakaya. Pyao kumakapala Epesalome baa ralo pao yuu Gesu dokona ee kana rema nembo kareya. Kareyamo dokopa Joape baame Dapiti kongo pyuo Epesalome anda epenale lena leya.
\c 14
\p 
\v 21 Enakana kiŋi dokome Joape lamaiyuo lao, Embame piso sipinyi dokona nambame piru lao suu pyapu. Emba papala akali parange Epesalome doko nyepala minyuo dae ipupi, leya.
\p 
\v 22 Dokopa Dapiti peteyamo lenge kambusa Joapeme yuu dokona pangu sepala lao, Emba kiŋi andake doko Anatumi emba elyape keta pisinya. Embame nambana piso sipunu dokona kapa lao sakapi dokona epapu embame namba rae mailini doko namba silyu, leya.
\v 23 Lapala Joape baa sipurapala yuu Gesa papala Epesalome nyuo minyuo Jerusaleme epeya.
\v 24 Dokopa kiŋi dokome Epesalome baa kiŋinya anda dokona pali nara lao lalu lao leya. Lapala lao, Baame Epesalome kanda naro daa, leya. Dokona Epesalome baa rangena anda palu karapala kiŋi peteya dokona epo maro laope pii naya.
\s1 Dapitimi Epesalome Koo Piya Dupwa Kame Sakamiya
\p 
\v 25 Epesalome baa akali ama keyange Isaraele wambu dupwame baa kando lakanda minya minya pingi. Banya yongo peparae kombe palyuope pii nange.
\v 26 Banya kyawa dokona kyawasi ama malu karo dee ama londe wakasa kenda pingi. Dokome ee kana yaka lao yuu mendaki larapu pyakepo rokonge. Kyawasi romende doko kiŋinya sikyali pingi dokona sikyali kilokerame lama ingiya.
\v 27 Epesalome baa wane rema mandenge. Dee wanake mendaki baa ama elyape keyange wakasa kingi Tama lenge manjo pingi.
\p 
\v 28 Epesalome baa kiŋi doko kanda nao ee kana lama Jerusaleme palyuo kareya.
\v 29 Karapala enakana baame Joape baa kiŋi doko petamo dokona pena lao piso serowaleŋe nyela pena lao akali lapo nembeya. Dopa piyamopape Joape baa epa naya. Epesalomeme kambako nyela pena leya. Dee kambako Joape simbi simbi pyuo epa naya.
\v 30 Dokopa Epesalomeme banya kendemande akali dupwa lamaiyuo lao, Kandalapa, Joapena ee yuu doko nambana repeta silyamo dokona bali jingi ando karamo. Dokona papala isare palyinya leya. Dokona lao nakama papala ee yuu dokona isare palyiyami.
\p 
\v 31 Doko sepala Joape baa Epesalomena anda papala lamaiyuo lao, Akipamo embena kendemande akali dupwame nambana ee yuu dokona isare palyalamisi? leya.
\p 
\v 32 Epesalome isingi lao, Doo pimi renge doko nambame emba nyela pena lapu doko emba epa napi dokona pimi, leya. Lapala lao, Nambame emba kiŋi doko petamo dokona papala piso sakao, Namba akipamo yuu Gesa doko yaki nyuo dae epeyose? Namba doo kareyoli doko keyange ingyapyali lapya lakapili lao suu piyu. Lapala deeko lao, Namba kiŋi doko kandala pare lao embame kiŋi dokome yuu gii mende jinya lao piso sakape. Dokopa namba keta koo mende palira ramo doko kiŋi dokome namba pyao kumakana, leya.
\p 
\v 33 Dokopa Joape baa kiŋi Dapiti peteyamo dokona papala Epesalomeme leyamo dupwa baa lamaiya. Dopa pyuo lamaiyasa kiŋi dokome Epesalome banya anda epena nyela pena leya. Leyasa Epesalome nyela peyaminyipa kiŋi peteyamo dokona lenge kambusa epapala yuu dokona pangu siya. Dokopa kiŋi dokome baa nyinyi pyuo yako lao nyiya.
\c 15
\s1 Epesalome Baame Dapitinya Kiŋi Yulu Isa Nembalana Leya
\p 
\v 1 Dokopa enakana akali Epesalome baa rangena mename ipyuo uliuli piso paenge mende nyuo dee mena ose lapo nyuo piya. Dee yanda singi akali akalisa kingi paki (50) baa paramo dokona role pyao baa lanyuo parami dupwa nyiyako.
\v 2 Baa wamba kukwa dokopa sipurarapu yuu taone dokona kame kambu dokona karapapu piya. Wambu mendepe dee wambu lamape imbu laiya lapala kote lao kiŋi dokome soo rolena lao epeyami. Dokopa Epesalome baame wambu doo epeyami dupwa kee lapala baame anja range lao piso sepa piya. Dokopa wambu dupwame isingi lao, namba yuu dusa rangeŋe rara dokonaŋa lapa piyami.
\v 3 Dokopa Epesalome baame lao, Embena pii doko rolae ingyuo silyamo. Dokona kiŋi dokome akali mende embena pii sakara doko rombo palya naya, leya.
\v 4 Dokopa Epesalome baame konda pyuo lao, Namba kote singi akali ingyapuli lao suu pyakonda pilyu. Dokona namba dopale karapuli doko wambu mendali pii dopale palipyali soo rolakamirunupa pii dupwa rolasi sipyali, leya.
\v 5 Dokopa akali mendeme Epesalome peteya dokona repeta papala pangu sepa piya dokopa Epesalome banya kingi pyasinju lapala akali doko kupyuo nyepala nyinyi pipa piya.
\v 6 Dokopa Epesalome baame Isaraele peparae kiŋi peteya dokona kote sakana lao epeyaminyi dupwa kando dopa pirapu piya. Dopa pyuo wambunya mona dupwa pyao kui leyasa baa kando mona maiyuo rae wakasa maiyami.
\p 
\v 7 Ee kana kisima epo papeyamo dokopa Epesalome baame kiŋi Dapiti kando lao, Kiŋi namba yuu Eperone dokona Kamongo doko kando lalu lao pii leyonoli pyuo piri lao namba puu lape.
\v 8 Namba yuu Gesu yuu Siria dokona singi yuu dokona paleyo dokopa nambame Kamongo kando lalu lao lao, Baame namba yuu Jerusaleme kamba kapu kyuo lanyuo para ramo doko nambame baa yuu Eperone dokona lakandaro, leyo, leya.
\p 
\v 9 Dokopa kiŋi dokome baa lamaiyuo lao, Manda rao mona seramo pupi leya dokome Epesalome baa yuu Eperone dokona peya.
\v 10 Dopa pyuo peyamopape baame wai pii minyingi akali lapome Isaraele rara peparae dapa lena lao lamaiyala pena, leya. Nakama bikuli pii poraiyuo ketae laramo siyami kande doko Epesalome baa yuu Eperone dokona kiŋi karamo lalapape lena lao lamainya, leya.
\v 11 Epesalome baame akali andete lama (200) baa role pyao Jerusaleme piso mona epena leya. Dokopa baame mende pinya suu piyamo doko akali dupwa see nayami.
\v 12 Baa mena pyao kiso maiyuo karo dokopa kiŋi Dapitinya dopa pyuo piri dapa pyuo piri lao nyiso lenge akali Ayitopele lenge doko Epesalome baame taone yuu Gaelo dokona nyela pena leya. Dokopa akali Ayitopele lenge doko epeyamopa kiŋi Dapitinya yulu isa nembalana lao yalu pyuo leyaminyi doko ama wakasa ingyuo lao andakiyami. Dopa piyamosa wambu Epesalome kando rae maiyami dupwa malu ingiya.
\s1 Dapiti Jerusaleme Yaki Nyuo Ralo Makando Peya
\p 
\v 13 Wai pii minyingi akali mendeme Dapiti dopa lamaiya. Isaraele wambu dupwame Epesalomena pii dokona soo rape rape lao kararama lao lalu lao letaminyi, leya.
\p 
\v 14 Dokona lao Dapitimi banya akali mupwa lapo baa role pyao yuu Jerusaleme dokona kareyami dupwa lamaiyuo lao, Namwa akali Epesalome dokome pyaa nana lao range kyawa lete nyelana suu pyapala dokopa yuu gii dakepako yuu mendasa mwua. Mende dee baa dae repe palipala namwa pyao isa palyapala wambu peparae yuu taone dokona petaminyi dupwa pyasaramiŋi yapa mwua, leya.
\p 
\v 15 Dokopa nakamame isingi lao, Waa emba kiŋi andake doko, embame aki mende larene dupwana namwame mee pirama, leyami.
\v 16 Dopa leyamisa kiŋi Dapiti baape banya ree palu dupwape dee banya akali mupwa dupwape peparae yuu Jerusaleme yaki nyuo peyami. Papala banya enda lapo konda pyuo nyiyamo akalisame banya yuu andape dupwa isako karena, leya.
\p 
\v 17 Lapala kiŋi baape dee wambu peparaepe Jerusaleme yaki nyuo peyami. Pao nakama yuu taone dokona wangu dusa anda mende kareyamo dokona imambu siyami.
\v 18 Dokopa banya akali mupwa dupwa peparae baa peteyamo dokona repeta karapala dokopa akali Keritena rarape dee akali Pilitena rarape epo peyaminyi dupwa kandeyami. Dokopa yuu Gati yanda singi akali andete pakinyamange (600) baa epeyamo dokona moko minyuo epeyami dupwa epo peyaminyi kandeyamiko.
\v 19 Dokopa kiŋi dokome nakamana akali mupwa Itai lenge doko kando lao, Emba akipamo namwa pipya epelese? Kapu kyuo papala kiŋi enenge dokopa pisa pupi. Emba akali yuu wakale range upinili. Wakale dupwame emba embena yuu rangena nyisa nembeyamisa epee kande leya.
\v 20 Emba dae yuu gii kuki lama palyuo karapi dokona nambapa akipamo awali lao mee dupwana papyuo kararambase? Namba anja pelyono lao namba kamame see nalyo. Dokona emba anda kapu kyuo pao dokopa embena akali role pyao epeyami dupwa opetae nyuo lanyuo pupi. Dokopa Kamongo dokome anjiki pyuo keyange ingyuo nakama poraiyuo nyiso rapu pyuo karena leto, leya.
\p 
\v 21 Dopa leyamopape Itai baame isingi lao, Emba kiŋi doko, nambame Kamongona kingi dokona lao lalu lao emba kando leto. Emba anja panda anja mendasa parene dupwana yuu peparae namba parambako. Dee emba pyao kumakarami ramo dokopa namba pyao kumakaramiko, leya.
\p 
\v 22 Dokopa Dapiti baa lamaiyuo, Kapaŋa. Epapu nakamame mona wambako pena, leya. Dopa leyasa Itai baape banya yanda singi dupwape dee nakamana ree palu wambupi wambo peyami.
\v 23 Dapitimoo banya wambu dupwa peparaepe yuu Jerusaleme yaki nyuo peyaminyi dokopa yuu dokona palenge wambu dupwa ee poraiyuo kaeyo leyami. Dokopa kiŋi doko ipwa kuki Kirone lenge doko yalo peyamo dokopa banya akali dupwa enakana yaloko peyami. Pao yuu muiyane dorena ingyuo peyami.
\p 
\v 24 Purisi akali mende Satoko lenge doko dokona kareya. Kareyamo dokona Lipae akali lapo role pyapeta kareyaminyi dupwame Kamongona Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko sakaro kareyami. Dokopa bokote doko isa reteyami. Dopa pipala wambu dupwa peparae yuu taone doko yaki nyuo pao oteyami dokopa enakana bokote doko nyepala soo peyami. Purisi akali Apiata lenge baa opetaeko dokona kareya.
\v 25 Dokopa kiŋi dokome akali Satoko doko lamaiyuo lao, Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko nyepala minyuo pao yuu taone dokona retala puu. Kamongo dokome namba kando rae maira ramo doko yuu gii mendepa bokote dokope dee seramo panda dokope kamba kapu kyuo kandala puu lara.
\v 26 Dee baame namba kando rae mai nara ramo doko kapako. Baame namba keta pinya suu pilyamo dupwa pinya, leya.
\v 27 Dee baame Satoko kando lao, Kanda. Embena ikinyi Aimase dokopa dee akali Apiatana ikinyingi Jonatane dokopa nyepala mona kyuu lao seramopa kamba kapu kyuo lanyuo yuu taone dokona pupi.
\v 28 Yuu gii dokopa namba yuu muiyane dokona ipwa yalo penge pona dokona isaro kararono pao embena pii mende namba sepala dokopa kaeyaro, leya.
\v 29 Dokona lao akali Satoko dee Apiatapame Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote doko soo kamba kapu kyuo Jerusaleme papala kareyambi.
\p 
\v 30 Dapiti baa yuu Olipi kyau dokona ee lao pulyuo peya. Baa kimbu suu pii nao kondome kumuo mona rando kyawasi yambe pyapala peya. Wambu lapo baa moko minyuo peyaminyi dupwa opetae dopako pyuo kyawa yambe pyao ee lao pulyuo peyami.
\v 31 Dokopa akali Ayitopele doko akali Epesalome dokome Dapitinya kiŋinya yulu isa nembalana leyamo dokona rae mailyamo lao lamaiyaminyi Dapiti siya. Sepala baame ateŋa lao lao, Kamongo, akali Ayitopele pii dopa pinya dapa pinya laramo dupwa kopyali ingyuo pena lao kyawa sisingi bolombalo lanyi nembape, leya.
\p 
\v 32 Dapiti yuu kyau ketae lakandenge panda angi doko kando nyela peyamo dokopa banya mona reto puu minyingi akali Asai lenge yuu Aki range dokome banya komau dupwa minyuo pilyuo awai kyawasinya pyao pipala peteyamo kando nyiya.
\v 33 Kando nyepala Dapitimi baa lamaiyuo lao, Emba namba role pyao epare ramo doko embame namba nyisa nare ingilyamo, leya.
\v 34 Dopa pirinyipape embame namba nyiso yuu taone dokona kapu kyuo papala akali Ayitopele kiŋi doko kando pii dopa pinya dapa pinya lao lenge dupwa pipya pimwaiyuo role karape. Karapala Epesalome lamaiyuo, Emba Kamongo doko. Nambame embena rakanena pii soo yulu pyuo kareyono doko suu pyao epapu nambame embena lao pyakaro, lena leya.
\v 35 Dokopa purisi akali Satoko Apaitapa dokona kararambi lyakande. Dokopa embame kiŋinya anda piso pii serene dupwa peparae kaeya nao akali dolapo lamaipi.
\v 36 Nakamba nakambana ikinyingi Aimase Jonatanepa reto karambinyi dokome emba pii serene dusipa peparae nyuo simu pyao maipala nakambame namba langyala pena lare, leya.
\p 
\v 37 Akali Epesalome doko epeyamo dokopa Dapitinya puu minyingi akali Asai doko kapu kyuo yuu taone dokona epeya.
\c 16
\s1 Akali Sipame Dapiti Kandala Peya
\p 
\v 1 Dapiti baa yuu kyau ketae yaki nyepala lupyuo donorena peyamo dokopa aopa Mipiposetana kendemande akali Sipa lenge dokome baa kando nyiya. Sipa baame borete andete lamape isa girapo jingi yando enge kareta andete mendakipi dee isa jingi kana poo renge simu pyasi andete mendakipi menana yanengeme pee wasisi ipwa waene paleta mendepe pipala dupwa peparae mena donge lamana retapala minyuo epeya.
\v 2 Epeyamo dokopa kiŋi Dapitimi baa piso soo lao, Bange dupwame peparae emba apa pirisi? leya.
\p Dokopa Sipame isingi lao, Mena donge dupwa embena ree palu dupwana piso papirami. Nenge boretepe isa jingipi akali dupwa narami. Dee ipwa waene doko nakama yuu muiyane dokona pao maka piramo dokopa narami, leya.
\p 
\v 3 Dokopa kiŋi dokome baa piso soo lao, Embena akali mupwa Solena kauwange Mipiposeta lenge baa anja karase? leya.
\p Leyamo dokopa Sipame isingi lao, Banya kauwange Solena kiŋi yulu doko rolo otapala Isaraele wambu dupwame baa keta jimili lao suu pyapala baa Jerusaleme dokona karamo, leya.
\v 4 Dokopa kiŋi dokome Sipa lamaiyuo lao, Bange peparae Mipiposetana ingyuo singi dupwa embena ingyara, leya.
\p Dokopa Sipame isingi lao, Namba embena kendemande akali. Emba kiŋi andake doko, nambame yuu peparae emba rae mainyi pyambuo karapuli yaka leto, leya.
\s1 Akali Simaimi Dapiti Kando Pii Koo Leya
\p 
\v 5 Kiŋi Dapiti baa yuu Bakurimi dokona pao pyaka siyamo dokopa akali mende Solena ree palu karengende kingi Simai lenge akali Gerana ikinyingi dokome baa kando nyepala randa maiyuo koo keta palyuo lao nembeya.
\v 6 Dopa pipala Dapiti baa banya akali dupwape dee banya isingi akali dupwamepe nyuo kako pyao nee piyaminyipape Simai baame kana lapo nyepala Dapitimoo banya akali mupwa pipya peyaminyi dokona pyao pyambuo piya.
\v 7 Pyapala baame lao nembo lao, Emba neta puu. Emba wambu pyao kumakange akali doko. Emba akali koo pingi doko. Emba puu pao puu, leya.
\v 8 Emba Solena panda nyepala kiŋi ingyuo karene. Dopa pipala Solena ree palu wambu malu pyao kumakalene. Dokona Kamongo dokome emba soo otapala emba nyuo alowa pipala embena ikinyi Epesalome doko namwa Isaraele wambunya kiŋi ingyuo karena lao romba palyapya. Emba wambu pyao kumungi dokona Anatumi emba pyao kokwa soo nembalopyamo, leya.\fig Simai baa pii koo dupwa lao kanape yuu kukipi dupwa pyao pyambuo piya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="16:13"\fig*
\p 
\v 9 Akali Apisai lenge enda Seruyana ikinyingi dokome kiŋi doko kando lao, Emba kiŋi andake doko. Akipamo akali kopyali dakeme suwa ingyuo randa jinya lao kaelese? Namba dokona dumu pao banya mange puku pyala puu larene, leya.
\v 10 Kiŋi dokome akali Apisaipa dee banya yangonge Joapepa kando lao, Doko nakambana yulu mende daa. Kamongo dokome pinya lao lamairamo dokona baa namba randa jera ramo doko api rolae pingipi mendeme piso soo akipamo pilyamo larami ingilyase? leya.
\v 11 Dokopa Dapitimi akali Apisaimoo banya akali mupwa dupwape peparae lamaiyuo lao, Namba rangena ikinyingi dokome namba pyao kumakalana pilyamo dokona akipamo Benjamenena rara dokona akali dakeme doo pilyamo dokona kando yamarangyuo mona nembaramisi? leya. Kamongo dokome namba kando pinya lao pii koo dupwa lena lao lamaipyamo pilyamo dokona baa yaki nyuo panda maiyuo yulu koo doko pinya kaeyalapape, leya.
\v 12 Kamongo dokome nambana mona randalyo doko kandapala namba koo keta palyuo pii lapyamo doko alowa pyuo namba elyape keta pisara rapisi.
\v 13 Dokona lao Dapitimoo banya akali dupwape kata nyuo peyaminyi dokopa Simai baa yuu kyau kipwa kipwa dorena kanda kanda pyuo paowali pyuo karo dokopa pii koo dupwa lao kanape yuu kulipi dupwa pyao pyambuo piya.
\v 14 Dokopa kiŋi dokope banya akali dupwape pao ipwa Jotane doko kando nyiyami. Dopa pyuo nakama kata pao karo maka pyuo kimbu randa pyuo piyasa ipwa mare dokona imambu soo peteyami.
\s1 Epesalome Jerusaleme Kareya
\p 
\v 15 Akali Epesalomemoo dee Isaraele akali lapo baa role kareyami dupwa peparaepe Jerusaleme sukusa peyami dokopa akali Ayitopele baa opetae dokona role pyao kareyami.
\v 16 Dapiti banya mona kulisa reto puu minyingi akali Asai lenge dokome Epesalome kando nyepala lao, Kiŋi doko palu karalu karena. Kiŋi doko palu karalu karena, leya.
\p 
\v 17 Dokopa Epesalomeme Asai baa piso soo lao, Embena mona kulisa retenge dee embena puu minyingi Dapiti doko apa pipyase? Emba akipamo baa role pyao paa napisi? leya.
\p 
\v 18 Dokona Asaimi isingi lao, Namba apa pyuo parose? Namba Kamongomepe wambu dupwamepe dee Isaraele peparaemepe rombo palyiyaminyi kiŋi dokona daerename ingyuo karo.
\v 19 Nambana akali mupwa dokona ikinyingi dokona yulu pyakami naro ramo nambame apinya yulu pyakamirusi? Nambame embena rakanena yulu pyakamiyu doko suu pyao epapu nambame embena yulu pyakaro, leya.
\p 
\v 20 Dokopa Epesalomeme kapu kyuo Ayitopele piso soo, Epapu namwa dae karamano. Dokona namwame apa piramase? Embena suu pilini dupwa namba serole langipi, leya.
\p 
\v 21 Dokopa Ayitopeleme isingi lao, Embena rakanena enda lapo konda pyuo nyiyamo dupwa anda yuupi rapu pyuo petena lapala peyamo dupwa kepo pyuo nyela puu. Dokopa embame embena rakanepe kinyi angi nyisu piso yanda pimwai ingyapilyamo lao Isaraele peparaeme soo nyerami. Soo nyepala wambu peparae embena pii lareneli pyuo pyuo kararami, leya.
\v 22 Dokona lao nakamana kiŋinya anda dokona yangi ketae dulunya komau anda mende Epesalomena pyakamiyami. Dokopa wambu peparaena lenge kambu dokona andakare papala rakangena enda lapo konda pyuo nyiyamo dupwa pipya kepo pyuo nyiya.
\p 
\v 23 Yuu gii dusipana Ayitopelena pii leyamo dupwa sepala Anatumi lele leyasa wambu peparaeme moko minyuo piyami. Wamba Dapitimi warombo soo piya. Dee enakana Epesalome baame opetaeko warombo soo pinya piya.
\c 17
\s1 Asaimi Epesalome Minyoko Pyuo Kyambo Lamaiya
\p 
\v 1 Kuki enakana Ayitopeleme Epesalome lamaiyuo lao, Nambame akali taosande akalisa ipisu lama (12,000) rombo palyapala rengya kukwa akali dupwa pipya role pyao Dapiti paramo dokona moko minyuo parole.
\v 2 Baa makame kumuo mona kumapala yame yame laramo pisira. Mange dokopa baa pakame kumuo pisiramopa banya akali dupwa ralo parami. Dokopa nambame kiŋi doko iki pyao kumakaro.
\v 3 Enda akali nyingi dupwa kapu kyuo akalingi karenge dokona epenge dopale ingyuo akali menge dupwa lanyuo emba petene dokona eparo. Embame akali mendaki iki pyalena suu pyapi doko pyao kumakare ramo dokopa endakalipi menge dupwa yanda pii nao kapa palyuo kararami, leya.
\v 4 Leyamo dokopa Isaraele akali mupwa dupwamepe dee Epesalome baamepe pii doo leyamo doko keyange ingyuo pelyamo, lao siyami.
\p 
\v 5 Epesalome baame lao, Epapu Asai baa opetae epena lao kee lalapape. Laraminyi dokopa baame pii laramo dupwa namwa semanale, leya.
\v 6 Akali Asai doko epeyamo dokopa Epesalome baame lamaiyuo lao, Pii dake akali Ayitopele dokome namwa langipyaŋa. Namwa doko moko minyuo pemase? Dee daa ramo doko embame namwa apa pirami lao langipi, leya.
\p 
\v 7 Asaimi isingi lao, Pii Ayitopeleme epapu nakama langipya doko kwaelyamo, leya.
\v 8 Embena rakane dokope akali menge dupwape nakama yanda ama poraiyuo pyuo yanda nengena petenge doko emba silini. Dee nakama mena marakae dupwana yakane waa nyakamingi dokopa pondoma pyuo nalana pingi dopale ingilyaminyi. Dee embena rakane doko yandana yulu soo oto pyuo retenge dokome baa kukwa dokopa banya akali dupwa pipya pali nange doko emba silini.
\v 9 Epapu dakepa baa kananda mendenape panda yuu mendasa yalu pyuo sera ramo soo pilyamo. Dopa pipala Dapiti baame aopa embena akali dupwa minyarapala pyara. Dopa pyuo pilyamo laraminyi sepala wambu dupwame embena akali dupwa pyao anamasi minyuo isa palyilyamo larami.
\v 10 Dapitimi dopa piramo dokopa embena rakane doko yanda singi andake wakasa dee banya akali dupwa yandana soo otenge doko Isaraele wambu peparae soo otelyaminyi dokona mena laeneme bange mendepe paka nange dopale ingyuo yanda singi porai yanda pingi dupwa pakao pyuo penge dupwa mee pakarami.
\v 11 Dokona nambana mana pii emba langilyu doko. Yuu pinjingi pakirena piso pao yuu pinjingi paki suu lao Isaraele akali peparae ipwa kee ipwa kota marengena singi dopale ingyuo nyuo pyasape. Pyasapala nakama lanyuo emba rangeme Dapitinya lenge kambu dokona yanda pela pupi, leya.
\v 12 Namwame Dapiti baa yuu anja angi karamo doko koto nyerama. Koto nyepala namwame Dapiti baape banya akali dupwape mende piraŋa lao see nao kamenge kararaminyipa namwame nakama pyarama. Namwa Dapiti baape banya akali dupwape peparae pyao kumakarama dokopa mendepe lete kara nara.
\v 13 Baa yuu taone mendena pao yalu pira ramo doko namwana wambu dupwame puu londe lapo minyuo epapala yuu taone doko puu dokome palyuo awali lapala ipyaraminyi dokopa lalyuo isa yuu pau lama lama dokona para. Dokopa kana kuki mendepe yuu kyau ketae dokona see nara, leya.
\p 
\v 14 Akali Epesalomemoo dee Isaraele akali peparae dupwame lao, Akali Ayitopelena pii doko keyange ingyapyamopape akali Asainya doko ama keyangelyamo, leyami. Kamongome akali Ayitopelena pii keyange doko minyuo pii narami dokopa randa andake doko akali Epesalome keta epara lao soo nyiya.
\s1 Dapiti Baa Repe Repe Pii Soo Kyawa Lete Nyuo Peya
\p 
\v 15 Enakana Asai baame mana pii akali Epesalomemoo Isaraele akali mupwa dupwape lamaiyamo dokope dee Ayitopeleme lamaiyamo dokope purisi akali Satokopa Apiatapa lamaiya.
\v 16 Dokopa Asaimi konda pyuo lao, Epapu waiya lao Dapiti keta pii wai nembapala yuu muiyane ipwa keno paenge doko yuu gii kukwa mende nembo pali nana. Epapu dakepa baape banya akali dupwa pipya peparae nyepala pyao kumaka nanaleŋe dakepa aopa ipwa Jotane doko yalo pena lena, leya.
\p 
\v 17 Dokopa akali Apiatana ikinyingi Jonatanepa dee akali Satokona ikinyingi Aimasepa yuu Jerusaleme repeta yuu Enerokele lenge dokona isaro kareyambi. Doko nakamba taone dokona sukusa parambano dokopa wambu dupwame kandasarami lapala piyambi. Dokopa kendemande wanakendeme mende piyamo dokopa yuu peparae lao nakamba lamairapu piyamosa nakambame pao kiŋi Dapiti lamaila parapu piyambi.
\v 18 Dopa piyambinyipape yuu gii mendepa wane mendeme nakamba kandapala baame akali Epesalome lamaiyamosa nakamba yuu Bakurimi dokona akali mendena anda papala waiya lao yalu pela peyambi. Dokopa banya anda repeta dusa banya yuwale singindena nakamba dokona koko pao yalu pyuo peteyambi.
\v 19 Dokopa akali dokona etenge dokome bange komau porai lapo nyepala yuwale kambu dokona yambe piya. Pyapala wambu mendemepe soo giso kanda naramiŋi lapala nenge witi jingi dupwa ketae dokona minyuo raeyo reteya.
\v 20 Dokopa Epesalomena akali mupwa dupwa anda dokona epapala enda doko piso soo lao, Aimase Jonatanepa anja karambisi? leyami.
\p Dokopa enda dokome isingi lao, Nakamba ipwa doko yalo papambi, leya.
\p Dokopa akali dupwame nakamba koto peyami. Peyaminyipape koto kando nyii napala nakama kapu kyuo Jerusaleme peyami.
\v 21 Enakana nakama yaki nyuo peyaminyi dokopa Aimase Jonatanepa yuwale dokona peteyambi doko nyisa epeyambi. Epapala pii dupwa Dapiti lamaila peyambi. Akali Ayitopeleme baa keta yanda pyuo pii lao reteyamo dupwa lamaiyambi. Lamaipala lao, Waiya lao ipwa doko yalo pupi, leyambi.
\v 22 Dokopa Dapitimoo banya akali dupwa pipya ipwa Jotane doko yalo peyami. Pao yuu yango rali dokopa nakama peparae ipwa dumurena yalo pao oteyami.
\p 
\v 23 Dokopa akali Ayitopele banya pii leyamo dupwa moko minyuo pyakami nayamisa banya mena donge doko nyepala piso para dokona rapa rapa pipala banya rangena yuu taone dokona peya. Enakana banya rangena yuupi bangepe dupwa peparae rapa rapa pyuo rolo otapala baa rangeme puu neya. Dopa piyamosa banya wambu ree palu malu pingi yuu dokona malu piyami.
\p 
\v 24 Akali Epesalomemoo Isaraele akali dupwa pipya Dapiti pyala pao ipwa Jotane doko yaleyami yuu gii dokopa Dapiti baa pao yuu taone Makanaimi lenge dokona pyaka siya.
\v 25 (Dokopa Epesalomeme akali Joapena panda nyuo akali Amasa doko yanda singi ami dupwana mupwa ingyuo isinya lao rombo palyiya. Amasa baa Isimaelena rara akali Jeta lenge dokona ikinyingi. Banya endangi doko Apikale lenge, Apikale baa akali Nasena wanenge dee akali Joapena endangi Seruya lenge dokona kakingi.)
\v 26 Epesalomemoo dee banya akali dupwa pipya yuu Giliate dokona komau anda pyuo paleyami.
\p 
\v 27 Yuu gii dokopa Dapiti baa yuu Makanaimi epeyamo dokopa akali remame baa kando nyiyami. Akali Sopi Nasena ikinyingi yuu taone Orapa Amone singi dokona rangepe Maka Amielena ikinyingi yuu taone Lotepa rangepe dee Basilai yuu Orokelimi yuu Giliate singi dokona rangepe dusipame kando nyiyami.
\v 28-29 Kando nyepala nakamame Dapitimoo banya akali dupwapena perepe penge warame wasisipi luu palenge komaupi nengepe minyuo epo maiyami. Dopa pyuo nenge witi jingipi bali jingipi palawape witi kisasipi mee binipi dee bini piipi amburali ipwangepe bulamakao susu ipwangepe dee nenge wasisi sisi lengepe mena sipisipi lapope dupwa peparae minyuo epo maiyuo piyami. Doko Dapitimoo banya akali dupwape yuu muiyane dokona kata papipala lopome kumuo ipwa nano kumuo maka pipyamo epelyaminyi lao soo nyepala nenge maiyami.
\c 18
\s1 Joapeme Epesalome Pyao Kumakaya
\p 
\v 1 Kiŋi Dapitimi banya akali dupwa peparae nyuo malu palyiya. Palyapala akali dupwa lili pirapu akali taosande mendaki lili wakale piya dee andete mende ingyarapu lili wakale pirapu karo piya. Dopa pipala akali mupwa iso laminyaraminyi dupwa lili dupwana mendaki larapu karo peya.
\v 2 Dopa pipala yanda angi pyala pena lao dokopa baame liti remana ingyuo wakale wakale akali Joapemoo dee Joapena yangonge akali Apisaimoo dee yuu Gati range akali Itaimoome pipya role pyao laminyuo iso pena, leya. Lapala kiŋi dokome banya akali dupwa lamaiyuo lao, Namba range nakama pipya role pyao paro, leya.
\p 
\v 3 Dokopa nakamame isingi lao, Emba namwa pipya epa nare. Namwa lapo kapu kyuo ralo makando paramanopape panda pingisi paki pyao kumakaraminyipape dokona nyisu petenge dupwa keta mende ingya nara. Dopa piramopape emba angingyuo pyalena lao karaminyi. Renge doko embame kyawa nyepala namwa taosande akalisa (10,000) ingilini. Dokona emba mee yuu taone dakena piso kaepala namwa nyisaramili lapo peyarapu pepe, leyami.
\p 
\v 4 Dokopa kiŋi dokome isingi lao, Nakamame mende keyange lao suu pyaraminyi doko nambame piru, leya. Lapala baa kame kambu kii wangu dokona kareyamopa banya akali dupwa kimbu pyao piso liti taosande mende ingyarapu andete mende ingyarapu pyuo peyami.
\v 5 Baame akali Joapemoo Apisaimoo dee Itaimoo pii lamaiyuo lao, Nambana kingi dokona lao akali parange Epesalome doko randa maiyaka nana, leya. Doko Dapitimi banya akali mupwa dupwa peparae pii dake lamaiyamopa yanda singi dupwa peparaeme soo oteyami.
\p 
\v 6 Dokopa Dapitinya yanda singi ami dupwa pao yuu kipwa kipwa dorena papala yuu Eporaime imwa dokona nakama Isaraele pipya yanda piyami.
\v 7 Dapitinya akali dupwame Isaraele akali dupwa pyao wini piyami. Dopa pyuo yanda isare rao pipala pyao wini piyaminyipa yuu gii dokopako akali ama malu taosande akalisa (20,000) kumuyami.
\v 8 Yuu muu kipwa kipwa dokona yanda doko pyuo andakyapala akali yandana kumuyaminyipape daa mee lapo kamame wakasa ingyuo imwa dokona kumuo peyami.\fig Banya ayemba rambuki nyepala mee yukwaro kareya.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="18:9"\fig*
\p 
\v 9 Dokopa aopa akali Epesalome dokome Dapitinya akali lapo kando nyiya. Epesalome baa mena donge matana piso peya. Pao isa kameya mende oke lenge kareya dokona isa lungwa lungwarena peyamosa isa wangya dokome banya ayemba rambuki nyepala mee yukwaro kareya. Dokopa mena donge doko makandoko peyamopa baa yeelyo isa dokona pero kareya.
\v 10 Dokopa Dapitinya akali dokona mendeme kandapala akali Joape doko kando lamaiyuo lao, Nambame Epesalome baa isa oke mendena yukwaro karapyamo kandapu, leya.
\p 
\v 11 Dokopa Joapeme isingi lao, Embame kandapala dokopa akipamo aopa pyao kumaka napisi? Embame baa pyapili doko namba rangeme emba kana kulingi akalisa dee marapu mende pipala emba jipuli, leya.
\v 12 Dopa leyamopape akali dokome isingi lao, Embame namba kana kulingi taosande mendaki jipilinyipape nambame kiŋinya ikinyingi doko yango palyili lao nambana kingi kuki dokona mendeme minyalyuo pyaa napuli, leya. Doko kiŋi dokome lao, Nambana lao suu pyao akali parange Epesalome doko randa maiyaka nalapape, lao embamoo akali Apisaimoo dee Itaimoope pii lao langiyamo doko namwa peparae siyama kande.
\v 13 Kiŋi baame mende pingi dupwa peparae soo otenge dokona nambame banya pii warombo see napala baa pyapuli doko dopa pyuo pyapi lao pii baa sipyali. Sepala baame namba randa jipyali embame namba nyisa napili, leya.
\p 
\v 14 Dokopa Joapeme lao, Yuu gii malu nembo namba embapa pii laa naramba, leya. Lapala Epesalome baa isa oke dokona lete yukwaro kareyamopa kaku rema nyepala Epesalomena kyangali dokona pyao pisiya.
\v 15 Dokopa Joapena yanda singi akali akalisame karo awali lapala Epesalome baa angi pyao kumakayami.
\p 
\v 16 Doko Joapeme yanda piyama doko kaena lao bikuli poo lena leyamo dokopa banya yanda singi malumi Isaraele dupwa peta ralyuo piyami dupwa yaki nyuo kaepala anda epeyami.
\v 17 Dokopa nakamame akali Epesalomena yongo doko nyepala imwa dokona yuwale kyuwa mendena malyiyami. Malyapala kana malumi ama ketae reto yambe pyao pulyuo nyiyami. Dokopa Isaraele akali peparae mendaki mendaki lao nakama rangena anda dupwana ralo makando peyami.
\p 
\v 18 Epesalome banya kingi dokona lao mendeme panda nyera wane ikinyingi mende manja naya dokome baa lete kareyamo yuu gii dokopa banya kingi doko ota naramopa suu pyao kararamiŋi lao kana londe mende Kiŋinya Yuu Pau Lama Lama dokona yuu apu rao pisiya. Pisiyamo yuu gii dokona piso pao dakepape wambu dupwame kana doko Epesalomena Kana lenge.
\s1 Epesalome Kumuyamo Dokona Lao Dapiti Lamaiyami
\p 
\v 19 Dokopa akali Aimase Satokona ikinyingi dokome Joape lamaiyuo lao, Kamongo dokome banya nyisu petenge dupwa pipya kiŋi doko kyawa lete nyuo nyisapyaŋa lao wai pii keyange doko minyuo kiŋi petamo dokona lamaila makando paowa, leya.
\p 
\v 20 Dokopa Joapeme lao, Daa. Epapu emba wai pii keyange lapo minyuo paa nare. Doko kiŋinya ikinyingi doko kumapyamo dokona yuu gii mendepa emba minyuo pare. Epapu daa, leya.
\v 21 Dokona banya kendemande akali Itiopia range doko lamaiyuo lao, Emba doo pipyamo kandapi dupwa kiŋi doko lamaiya puu, leya. Dokopa kendemande akali dokome Joape kando pangu sepala makando peya.
\p 
\v 22 Aimase suu lao lao, Namba mende pira dupwana mende masa nalyoŋo. Wai pii doko kamame minyuo parole, leya.
\p Dokopa Joapeme isingi lao, Nambana ikinyingi, emba dokona yano mende nyii nare doŋo akipamo dopa pinya suu pilisi? leya.
\p 
\v 23 Aimaseme kamba lao, Mende pira dupwana wari laa nalyo mee panya suu pilyu, leya.
\p Dokopa Joapeme lao, Doko kapaŋa puu, leya. Dokona lao baa kata dokona makando lupyapala yuu Jotane Pau Lama Lama dokona suku suku papala Itiopia akali doko yaki nyuo baa wambo peya.
\p 
\v 24 Yuu taone dokona kame kambu dowa kamandape dee andakarepe kanya iki siyamo dokona Dapiti baa peteya. Dokona yuu taonena kambu isingi akali mende kana kame doko ketae pulyuo peya. Papala kambu dorena ketae anda yangi ingyuo perao karenge dokona kareya. Karapala dokopa akali mende baa iki makando repeta repeta epeyamo doko kandeya.
\v 25 Kandapala baame isa kee lapala kiŋi doko lamaiya. Dokopa kiŋi dokome lao, Baa iki epara ramo doko baame wai pii keyange mende minyuo epara, leya. Dokopa akali makandeyamo doko makando repeta repeta epeya.
\p 
\v 26 Dokopa dee isingi akali dokome akali mendeko iki makando epeyamo kandeya. Kandapala baame akali kame kambu dowa dokona iso karenge doko kee lapala, Kanda. Akali mendeko makandelyamo, leya.
\p Dokopa kiŋi dokome isingi lao, Akali dokome opetae wai pii keyange mende minyuo epelyamo, leya.
\p 
\v 27 Dokopa isingi akali dokome lao, Nambame kandapu dokopa akali wambo makandapya doko Aimasena makandenge dopale ingyapya, leya.
\p Dokopa kiŋi dokome lao, Baa akali keyange. Baame wai pii keyange mende minyuo epo pilyamo, leya.
\p 
\v 28 Dokopa Aimaseme kiŋi doko pii ketae palyuo yako lapala banya lenge kambu siyamo dokona pangu soo dopa lamaiyuo, Embena Kamongo Anatu lakando karape. Renge dokona lao akali dupwame emba kiŋi andake doko isa nembalana lao karaminyi dupwa keta baame anamasi minyingi renge doko jiya, leya.
\p 
\v 29 Dokopa kiŋi dokome piso soo lao, Akali parange Epesalome doko kapa lete karase? leya.
\p Aimaseme isingi lao, Kamongo, embena akali mupwa Joapeme namba puu lapyamo dokopa wambu peparae mona rando pii malu lao akema lalya lana pyuo karami. Doko piminyipape doko apa pipya lao namba langi nami, leya.
\p 
\v 30 Doko kiŋi dokome baa lamaiyuo lao, Dumbisa karena leya. Dokopa baa dokona papala kareya.
\p 
\v 31 Dokopa Itiopia kendemande akali doko epapala kiŋi doko lamaiyuo lao, Emba kiŋi andake doko, nambame wai pii keyange mende minyakao ipu. Epapu Kamongo dokome wambu emba kando pimwaiyuo nyuo isa palyalana kareyami dupwa isa palyuo anamasi minyakapya, leya.
\p 
\v 32 Dokopa kiŋi dokome piso soo lao, Akali parange Epesalome kapa lete karase? leya.
\p Dokopa Itiopia kendemande akali dokome isingi lao, Kamongo, baa keta mende pipyamo doko embena nyisu petenge dupwape dee emba mata joo penge dupwape peparae keta pipyali yaka lao suu pilyu, leya.
\p 
\v 33 Dokopa kiŋi doko baa wakasa mona randaya. Kame kambu penge dorena ingyuo panda kuki ketae dokona papala ee lao peteya. Baa pao dokopa ee dopa pyuo leya. O nambana ikinyingi, nambana Epesalome. Epesalome nambana ikinyingi. Namba embena panda doko nyepala kumapuli doko kapa ingyapyali. Nambana ikinyingi Epesalome, nambana ikinyingi, lao ee leya.
\c 19
\s1 Joape Dapiti Kando Pii Poraiyuo Leya
\p 
\v 1 Kiŋi Dapiti baa Epesalomena lao ee lao kumanda petamo lao Joape lamaiyaminyi siya.
\v 2 Kiŋi doko banya ikinyingi doko kondo kumanda petamo leyami doko sepala Dapitinya akali malu dupwa rae maiyuo wini pingi renge paleya doko alowa pipala mona randame kumuo kumandako peteyami.
\v 3 Nakama yanda singi dupwa yandana pakao nyisa papala elyapala elya kalo karenge dopale ingyuo yuu taone dokona elya kalo sukusa dee peyami.
\v 4 Dokopa kiŋi dokome banya lenge kambu yambe pyapala ee poraiyuo lao lao, O nambana ikinyingi. Nambana ikinyingi Epesalome. Epesalome nambana ikinyingi, lao ee leya.
\p 
\v 5 Dokopa Joape baa kiŋinya anda papala kiŋi doko kando lao, Epapu embena akali dupwa koo pepeya ingyuo wasinyi pyambuo pelyamo. Akali embena ikinyi wanenyepe lete nyiminyipape dee embena etene dupwape enda lapo konda pyuo nyingi dupwape lete nyiminyi dupwa koo inginyi nembapi kandapi.
\v 6 Embame wambu emba mona retaminyi dupwa kando yanda pimwailini. Dee emba kando rae mai nami wambu dupwa kando mona minyarambu karalene. Embena akali mupwa dupwape mee akali dupwape angi mende daa lao suu pilini. Nambame Epesalome baa epapu lete epapala namwa peparae kumamwali doko emba kuki rae maipili lamo lao kandelyo.
\v 7 Epapu papala embena akali dupwa anjiki pyuo pii lamaila pare. Dopa pii nare ramo doko nambame Kamongona kingi lao rakya yangama dokona mendaki mendepe embamoo role kara narami, leto. Emba palu karenge yuu gii dupwana randa andake koo nao palu karare, leya.
\v 8 Dokopa kiŋi doko roya karapala yuu taone dokona kame kambu repeta peteya. Banya akali dupwame baa dokona petamo leyami doko sepala nakama peparae dokona pao malu palyiyami.
\s1 Dapiti Kanda Soo Kamba Kapu Kyuo Jerusaleme Peya
\p Yuu gii dokopa Isaraele peparae ralo wakale wakale pyuo nakama rangena anda dupwana peyami.
\v 9 Yuu Isaraele dokona peparae nakama range lao laiya lao apyanda pyuo lao nakama range lao lao, Kiŋi Dapitimi namwana nyisu petenge dupwa pipya kyawa lete nyiya. Namwa Pilisitia wambu pipya kyawa lete nyiya kande. Epapu Epesalomena reke lao ralo papala yuu yaki nyuo pelyamo, leyami.
\v 10 Namwa akali Epesalome doko namwana kiŋi ingyara lao kyawa dokona mamba kulimbuo kisakamyuo rombo palyiyama. Dopa pyuo rombo palyiyamanopape baa yanda dokona piyaminyisa kumuya. Dokona lao akipamo mendeme kiŋi Dapiti doko kamba minyuo dae eparamo dokona lao laa nalyamisi? leyami.
\p 
\v 11 Pii doo Isaraele wambu leyaminyi doko Dapiti keta waiya lao peya. Dopa piyamosa baame purisi akali Satoko Apiatapame Juta akali mupwa dupwa piso sela pena leya. Isaraele akali namba kiŋi dee karapili lao suu pilyaminyipape akipamo nakama enakana kiŋi doko banya anda dokona minyuo eparami ingilyase?
\v 12 Nakama nambana ree palu, Nakama nambana yongo mendare dee ranjama mendaki. Dokona nakamame akipamo namba enakana lanyuo eparamisi? leya.
\v 13 Dapitimi Amasa lamainya lao lamaiyuo, Emba nambana ree palu. Epapu dakepa nambame emba Joapena panda joo yanda singi dupwana mupwa ingyuo karape leto. Nambame dopa pii naro ramo dokopa nambana Anatumi namba randa jinya leto, leya.
\v 14 Nakama Dapitinya pii doko sepala Juta akali peparae mona piyasa baa keta mona maiyuo pyamalyapala baamoo banya akali mupwa dupwa peparaepe kamba kapu kyuo epena leyami.
\p 
\v 15 Baa kapu kyuo epeyamo dokopa katasa ipwa Jotane pona dokona Juta akali lapo yuu Gilikale dokona kiŋi akali ipwa dokona yalo lanyala epeyaminyi dupwa kando nyiya.
\v 16 Yuu gii mendaki dokopako Benjamenena rara akali Simai lenge Gerana ikinyingi yuu Bakurimi range doko ipwa Jotane dokona Dapiti kando nyela epeya.
\v 17 Epo dokopa Benjamenena akali rara taosande mendaki (1,000) dee akali Sipa lenge Solena ree palu dokona kendemande karenge dokopa dee banya ikinyingi akalisa ipisu kingi paki dusipape dee banya kendemande akali akalisa lama pipala nyuo ipwa Jotane dokona kiŋi doko kando nyela epeyami. Epeyaminyi dokopa kiŋi baa banya akali dupwape ene epapa nayaminyisa nakama ipwa Jotane dokona epeyami.
\v 18 Nakama kiŋi andake dokope banya wambu pipya epeyaminyi dupwape ipwa doko yalo lanyala epo dee kiŋi dokome leyamuli pyuo pirama lao ipwa yalo peyami.
\s1 Dapitimi Simai Kando Anjiki Piya
\p Kiŋi doko ipwa dokona yalo panya rapa rapa piyamo dokopa akali Simaimi baa range pyakao papala kiŋinya lenge kambu siyamo dokona pangu siya.
\v 19 Sepala lao, Emba kiŋi andake doko, yuu Jerusaleme yaki nyinyi yuu gii dokopa nambame kopetame piyu doko nyuo kame sakape. Dokona dee nambapa yanda pimwaiyuo minyaro karo suu pyao karalu kara napipi.
\v 20 Namba koo piyuŋu doko namba silyu. Renge dokona namba mendaki dokoko yuu dulurena rara dokona piso epapu epapala emba kiŋi doko yako lao nyela epelyo, leya.
\p 
\v 21 Leyamo dokopa akali Apisai Seruyana ikinyingi dokome ketae palyuo pii lao, Kamongo dokome kiŋi karena lao wasiyamo doko keta koo mende palena leyamo dokona Simai baa pyao kumakamana, leya.
\p 
\v 22 Dopa leyamopape Dapitimi Apisaipa banya yangonge Joapepa lamaiyuo lao, Nakambana suu pingi doko apimi piso silyase? Nakambame namba randa jelana letambisi? Namba dake epapu Isaraele wambunya kiŋi ingyuo karo dokona epapu Isaraele wambu kuki mende kumunya lao randa mai narama, leya.
\v 23 Lapala baame Simai lamaiyuo lao, Nambame emba pyao kumaka narami lao lalu lao langilyu, leya.
\s1 Dapitimi Akali Mipiposeta Kando // Anjiki Piya
\p 
\v 24 Dokopa Mipiposeta Solena kauwange akali doko kiŋi doko yako lao nyela epeya. Doko baa kiŋi doko Jerusaleme yaki nyiyamo yuu gii dokopa Mipiposeta banya angasipi kyawasipi dupwa rokwa nao dee kimbu dupwa wate pii nao komau dupwa wate pii naope piyamopa pao kiŋi doko wini pipala kamba kapu kyuo epeya.
\v 25 Mipiposeta baa kiŋi doko yako lao nyero lao Jerusaleme piso epeyamo dokopa kiŋi dokome baa lamaiyuo lao, Mipiposeta akipamo emba nambapa role pyao epa naese? leya.
\p 
\v 26 Baame isingi lao, Emba kiŋi andake doko, nambana kimbu dolapo koo doko emba silini. Dokome namba embapa role pyao parambaŋa lapala nambana kendemande akali doko lamaiyuo, Nambana mena donge dokona piso embapa role parambaŋa komau kwuo rapa rapa pyakana leyonopape baame namba kyambo langipala pyaka naya.
\v 27 Emba kiŋi andake doko. Baame nambana lao kyambo langiya. Dopa leyamopape emba Anatunya aŋala dopale dokome embame kandarene rolara dupwa pepe.
\v 28 Emba kiŋi andake doko. Nambana rakanena ree palu dupwa peparae kokwa soo kumunginya pyambuili doko rolae ingiyali. Dopa piyamopape embame embena rate dokona nenge nala ipu lee kande. Emba kiŋi andake doko. Nambame emba keta anjiki pyuo nyisa laope bange mendepe jii lao piso serono kata mende see nalyamo, leya.
\p 
\v 29 Dokopa kiŋi dokome isingi lao, Emba dee kamba lama konda pyuo laa nare ingilyamo. Embapa Sipapa Solena bange dupwape dee yuu dupwape mokwa soo nyerambi lao suu pyao otapu, leya.
\p 
\v 30 Mipiposetame isingi lao, Sipa baa dupwa peparae nyinya kae, Emba kiŋi andake doko anda lete ipi dokona namba rae mailyu. Dokona mende nyii naro, leya.
\s1 Dapitimi Akali Basilai Kando Anjiki Piya
\p 
\v 31 Akali Basilai yuu Giliate range doko opetaeko yuu Orokelimi yaki nyuo kiŋi doko ipwa Jotane keno epena piyamo doko nyiso nyela epeya.
\v 32 Basilai baa akali alemo. Baa ee kana akalisa mange lama (80) ingiya. Doko baa ama akali kamongo ingyuo bange malu retenge. Dokome kiŋi doko yuu Makanaime dokona peteyamo dokopa nenge dupwa maiya epeya.
\v 33 Epeyamo dokopa kiŋi dokome baa lamaiyuo lao, Nambame emba rapu piruŋu Jerusaleme namba role pyao bona epena leya.
\p 
\v 34 Dopa leyamopape Basilaimi isingi lao, Namba yuu gii malu palu kara naro doŋo. Emba kiŋi andake dokopa namba akipamo Jerusaleme parambase? leya.
\v 35 Namba ee kana akalisa mange lama (80) karamo dokona dee bange mendeme namba rae mainyi pyambwa nara. Namba ipwa nengepe napu dupwana rende pingi palipyamo naa nalyo. Dee kenane pyami dupwa see nalyo. Emba kiŋi doko nambame emba randa jisasaroŋo daa leya.
\v 36 Nambame yano andake dupwa nyii naro ingilyamo. Dokona lao namba mee kuki lama emba role pyao ipwa Jotane keno unipili papala kaeyo emba puu larole, leya.
\v 37 Lapala nambana anda papala nambana ree palu dupwana malu anda repeta kumaro kapu kyuo parole. Dake nambana ikinyingi Kimikame lenge embena yulu pyakara. Emba role nyuo lanyuo pupi. Emba kiŋi andake doko, embame keyange lao suu pilini dupwa banya lao pyakamipi, leya.
\p 
\v 38 Kiŋi dokome isingi lao, Nambame baa lanyuo papala yulu embame pipili lao suu pilini dupwa piru. Dee embame mende pyaka lao piso serene dupwa pyakaro, leya.
\v 39 Dokopa Dapitimoo banya akali dupwa pipya ipwa Jotane doko yalo dumurena peyami. Dokopa baame akali Basilai doko nyinyi pipala yako lao elyape keta pisiyamopa anda kapu kyuo peya.
\s1 Juta Wambu Dupwape Isaraele Wambu Dupwape Kiŋi Dokona Lao // Apiyanda Piyami
\p 
\v 40 Kiŋi doko ipwa yalo oteyamo dokopa Juta akali peparaemepe dee Isaraele akali pingyasi lapomepe baa kako pyao nyiso minyuo peyami. Baa yuu Gilikale dokona peyamo dokopa akali Kimikame baa dokona role pyapeta peyambi.
\v 41 Dokopa Isaraele peparaeme kiŋi peteya dokona papala baa kando lao, Emba kiŋi andake dokope embena ree palu wambu dupwape embena akali dupwape akipamo namwana yangonge Juta akali dupwame keyange pilyamano lao suu pyao nakama nyepala Jotane yalo minyuo rapu pyuo pumisi? leyami.
\p 
\v 42 Juta akali dupwame isingi lao, Namwa doo pimwano doko kiŋi doko namwa pipya mendarendeme pimwaŋa. Dokome nakama akipamo imbu singi manjinyi pyambwarase? Baame namwa nenge ropo pyao joo dee bange mende joope pii napya, leyami.
\p 
\v 43 Leyaminyi dokopa Isaraele akali dupwame isingi lao, Kiŋi Dapiti baa nakamana rara angingyuo karapyamopape namwa rara akalisa karo nakama mendaki iki isa palyilyamano. Dokona lao akipamo nakamame namwa kilya kando lao karamisi? leyami. Lapala namwa wambo suu pyao kiŋi doko dae lanyala eparama lao leyama doko kame see nalapape, leyami.
\p Leyaminyipape Juta range dupwame Isaraele wambunya pii isa palyili lao poraiyuo leyami.
\s3 20:1—21:22 Yuu Isaraele dokona randa wakale wakale Dapiti keta epeya. Banya wambu lapo liti pyuo baa mata maiyuo kareyami. Dee lopo soo yanda pyuo kareyaminyipape Dapiti baa kapa palyuo kareya.
\c 22
\s1 Dapitimi Wini Pyuo Kenane Piya
\p 
\v 1 Kamongo baame Dapiti banya nyisu petenge akali Solemoo dee akali lapo dupwa keta baa kyawa lete nyiyamo dokona kenane dake Dapitimi Kamongo doko kando piya.
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Kamongo doko nambana kyawa lete nyuo alya isa ingingi akali.
\q1 Baa kame porai dopale ingyuo namba kako pyaro karenge.
\q1 
\v 3 Nambana Anatu doko nambana alya minyingi akali dokona
\q1 namba baa keta kyawa lete epelyo.
\q1 Baame konambe dopale ingyuo namba alya minyingi.
\q1 Dee baa nambana lete wai pyao nyingi akali
\q1 wambu dupwame namba pyalana randa jilyaminyi dokopa baame namba keta alya minyuo nyisingi.
\q1 
\v 4 Nambame Kamongo doko kee letono dokopa
\q1 baame nambana nyisu petenge dupwa keta kyawa lete nyuo nyisingi.
\q1 Dokona Kamongo lakandamanale.
\b
\q1 
\v 5 Ipwa kota kasakole minyuo ipwa marengena epenge dopale ingyuo kumungi renge dokome namba nyuo sukusa pyambuya.
\q1 Dee ipwa kasakole minyingi dopaleko ingyuo randa renge dupwame namba nyuo bwuakiki piya.
\q1 
\v 6 Kumungi rengena randa dokome namba keta kako piya.
\q1 Dokopa malu andana kone dokome nambana lao makaro siya.
\q1 
\v 7 Dokopa namba randa nao karo Kamongo doko kee leyo.
\q1 Nambame nambana Anatu doko nyisinya lao kee leyo.
\q1 Dokopa banya tembole anda dokona karo baame nambana pii soo
\q1 namba nyisinya lao ee leyono doko siya.
\b
\q1 
\v 8 Dokopa yuu dupwa pyuku pyuku lao romo romo piya.
\q1 Anatu baa imbwayamosa
\q1 yake doko ama romo romo piya.
\q1 
\v 9 Dokopa banya gyaa kata dokona isare sukwa potemo epeya.
\q1 Dee isare rao uliyapu nyingi lelenge dupwape dee sungwa lengya dupwape banya nenge kata dokona epeya.
\q1 
\v 10 Dokopa baame yake doko nyuo karalyapala
\q1 banya kimbu isarename kopa pupuri rau dokopa role pyapeta baa isa epeya.
\q1 
\v 11 Baa aŋala dokona mata dokona piso isa epeya.
\q1 Epapala baa poo raiyana papake dopale ingyuo dokona piso kata papiya.
\q1 
\v 12 Baa range iminjingi dokome yambe piya.
\q1 Dopa pipala baa kopa romende ipwa malu petenge dupwame baa keta piso kako piya.
\q1 
\v 13 Baa peteyamo dokona yuu pele pipala isareme rasi sungwa lengya dupwa lele pyao soo ketae peya.
\b
\q1 
\v 14 Dokopa Kamongo dokome yake dokona piso yuu gala leya.
\q1 Leyamo dokopa Anatu Porai Wakasa dokona pii doko wambu peparaeme siyami.
\q1 
\v 15 Akali mendeme banya nyisu petenge dupwa wanga dupwame pingi dokopa nakama ralo penge doko suu pyao
\q1 yuu pele piyamo dokopa banya nyisu petenge dupwa wakale wakale pyuo makando peyami.
\q1 
\v 16 Dokopa Kamongo dokome banya nyisu petenge dupwa kando mena nalena pingi ingyuo imbu singi manjo pii poraiyuo lao piyamopa
\q1 banya pii doko poo raiya andakeme bange minyalya minyana pingi doko suu pyao
\q1 ipwa kota pete isa donorename dupwa epo maro leya.
\q1 Dee yuu dokona isa susa pingi bange dupwa mee epo panembena siya.
\b
\q1 
\v 17 Kamongo dokome yake panda piso isa epapala namba nyiya.
\q1 Baame namba ipwa koko dupwana paleyono dokopa nyisa ipyuo nyiya.
\q1 
\v 18 Baame nambana nyisu petenge ama porai palenge dupwa keta baame kiiramo nyiya.
\q1 Dee lapome namba awa nayami dupwa keta opetaeko kiiramo nyiya.
\q1 Nakama ama porai wakasa dokome namba anamasi minyaro ingya nalyamo.
\q1 
\v 19 Namba randa nyuo kareyono dokopa nakamame namba minyarapala nyiyami.
\q1 Dopa piyaminyipape Kamongo dokome namba alya isa ingyuo kyawa lete nyiya.
\q1 
\v 20 Nambana randa epeya dupwana baame namba neta nyuo nyisiya.
\q1 Baame nambapa rae maiyuo epe kandeya dokome namba kyawa lete nyuo nyisiya.
\b
\q1 
\v 21 Namba rolae pingi dokona Kamongome namba yano pyakange.
\q1 Namba koo mende pii nange dokona baame namba elyape keta pisingi.
\q1 
\v 22 Nambame Kamongona lowa dupwa warombo singi.
\q1 Nambame nambana Anatu kando mata maiyuo kapu kyuo paa nange.
\q1 
\v 23 Nambame banya lowa dupwana peparae letamuli pyuo kando minyuo pyuo karenge.
\q1 Banya mawa pii dupwana namba kamba lao warombo see nangende daa.
\q1 
\v 24 Nambame koo mende pisarono kando lao nyokonyuo karenge
\q1 dee namba koo mende pii nange doko baa silyamo.
\q1 
\v 25 Dokona lao namba rolae pingi dokome baame namba yano jingi.
\q1 Renge doko baame namba keta koo mende pali nange doko baame soo gisingi.
\b
\q1 
\v 26 Kamongo wamba lapome emba poraiyuo suu pyao yaki nyii nao karenge dupwa kando
\q1 embame nakama keta lalu lao leeneli pyuo poraiyuo suu pyaoko karenge.
\q1 Dee wambu lapo kopetame pii nao kata rolae dokona iki pyuo karenge dupwa kando embame keyangeko pingi.
\q1 
\v 27 Wambu mendeme poo pyasi ingyuo karenge ramo doko keta embame baa embena poo pyasi renge doko lasaka pingi.
\q1 Dopa pinginyipape wambu mende yulu koo pingi ramo doko keta embame yano pyao randa maingi.
\q1 
\v 28 Embame wambu range kuki ingyuo inyimungu karenge dupwa kyawa lete nyingi.
\q1 Dopa pinginyipape wambu range mupwa lao suu pyao ulipili ingingi dupwa kando embame nyuo isa palyingi.
\b
\q1 
\v 29 Emba Kamongo doko, Nambana kendapulinya mendeke ingyuo karenge.
\q1 Dee embame namba keta iminjingi dupwa nyuo nembakapala yanganyi retakange.
\q1 
\v 30 Embame nambana nyisu petenge dupwa pyaa lao namba porainya renge jingi.
\q1 Dee embame namba porainya renge jingi dokopa nyisu petenge dupwana yuu taone dupwana kana kame dupwa mee pyao lalyuo kokwa soo nembenge.
\q1 
\v 31 Anatu doko, banya yulu pipyamo dupwa ama mondo lao rolae ingyuo pelyamo.
\q1 Dee baame mende lalu lao lapyamo pii dupwa kinyi angingyuo pelyamo.
\q1 Dopa pyuo wambu lapo baame kyawa minyinya lao koto parami ramo dupwa keta
\q1 baa konambe dopale ingyara.
\q1 
\v 32 Kamongo baa iki doko Anatu.
\q1 Dee Anatu baako nambwana nee isa ingyaro karamo.
\q1 
\v 33 Anatu doko namba porainyi pyambuo
\q1 namba anja panda anja dupwana penge dokopa iso karenge.
\q1 
\v 34 Baame namba mena diya lenge lukuma nao kata papingi dopale ingyuo papi lao pingi.
\q1 Dee namba yuu kyau dupwana kata papyuo karenge dokopa baame namba nyisingiko.
\q1 
\v 35 Doko yanda enekongo porai dupwa minyuo yanda piriŋi lapala
\q1 baame namba yanda dupwana mana langingi.
\b
\q1 
\v 36 O Kamongo, Embame namba alya isa ingyuo karo lete wai pyao nyingi.
\q1 Embena nyisapinyi renge dokome wambu peparaena lenge kambu dokona nambana kingi doko ando pelyamo.
\q1 
\v 37 Dopa pipala embame nambana yanda pimwai dupwame minyarapala nyisasarami lao iso karapinyipa
\q1 namba isa paa nange.
\q1 
\v 38 Nambame nyisu petenge dupwa peta ralyuo pyapala anamasi minyingi.
\q1 Nambame kaeya napala nakama pyao kokwa soo nembapala dokopa kaenge.
\q1 
\v 39 Dopa pipala nambame nakama pyao isa palyingi dokopa nakama sipuro epa nange.
\q1 Nakama nambana kimbu isarena kumasi singi.
\q1 
\v 40 Embame yandana namba porainya renge jingi.
\q1 Nambame nyisu petenge dupwa pipya pyao anamasi minyare lao nyisingi.
\q1 
\v 41 Embame nambana nyisu petenge dupwa namba kando makando pena lao pingi.
\q1 Dokopa wambu namba epe kanda nange dupwa nambame pyao kokwa soo nembenge.
\q1 
\v 42 Dokopa nakama wambu lapome nyisamili lao kotelyaminyipa mendemepe nakama kyawa lete nyuo nyisa nange.
\q1 Nakamame Kamongo doko nyisinya lao kee letaminyipape baame nakama isingi yano pyaa nange.
\q1 
\v 43 Nambame nakama pyao inji ranji pingi dokopa nakama sinjimu dopale ingingi.
\q1 Dopa pipala nambame nakama katana wara silyamopa kalyuo papingi dopale ingyuo isa palyingi.
\b
\q1 
\v 44 Embame wambu namba kando kamba lao mata joo kareyaminyi dupwa keta namba kyawa lete nyuo nyisingi.
\q1 Embame wambu rara peparae keta namba kiŋi kara lao rombo palyapala iso karenge.
\q1 Wambu namba kando see nange dupwame nambana yulu pyakalyaminyi.
\q1 
\v 45 Dopa pipala wambu yuu wakale range dupwame nambana lenge kambusa pangu singi.
\q1 Nakamame nambana pii sepala dokopa warombo singi.
\q1 
\v 46 Nakamana paka nange renge doko isa penge.
\q1 Dopa pilyamopa nakamana anda porai dokona piso walu walu lao nyisa epo nambana arapunya role pyao karala epenge.
\b
\q1 
\v 47 Kamongo doko lete karalu karenge.
\q1 Baa nambana nee isa ingyuo karenge doko lakandena.
\q1 Anatu porainya renge palenge dokome namba lete wai pyao nyingi dokona kingi ketae pena lao leto.
\q1 
\v 48 Nambame nyisu petenge dupwa isa palyuo anamasi minyare lao nyisingi.
\q1 Nyisapala baame wambu rara lapo dupwa namba isarena karena lao pingi.
\q1 
\v 49 Nambana nyisu petenge dupwa keta baame nyiso neta nyingi.
\q1 Kamongo nambana nyisu petenge dupwa isa palyuo anamasi minya lao nyisingi.
\q1 Embame namba alya isa minyuo karapinyipa akali wambu pyao randa maingi dupwame namba pyao kumaka nalyaminyi.
\b
\q1 
\v 50 Dokona lao wambu rara peparaena lenge kambusa karo nambame emba lakandelyo.
\q1 Nambame emba kando lakando kenane pilyu.
\q1 
\v 51 Namba banya kiŋi Dapiti dokome nyisu petenge dupwa anamasi minyare lao Anatumi porainya renge jingi ingyuo karenge.
\q1 Baame namba banya rombo palyiyamo akali doko mona kulisa retenge.
\q1 Dopa pipala namba Dapiti ketape dee nambana para pyaramo dupwa ketape mona reto karalu karara.
\c 23
\s1 Dapitinya Pii Lao Lumwa Pyuo Leya
\p 
\v 1 Dapiti akali Jesena ikinyingi dokome Kamongome mupwa inginyi nembeya. Akali doko Jekopena Anatu dokome baa kiŋi ingyuo rombo palyiya dokome kenane pii keyange dupwa Isaraele wambunya pyao retakamiya. Dokona pii dake Dapitimi lumwa pyuo leya.
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Kamongona Imambu dokome namba keta pii letamo.
\q1 Banya wai pii dupwa nambame lakare lao jingi.
\q1 
\v 3 Isaraele wambunya Anatu dokome pii leya.
\q1 Isaraele wambunya konambe ingyuo alya isa ingingi dokome namba langyuo lao,
\q1 Kiŋi akali kata rolae dokona iki wambu dupwa iso karo
\q1 dee Anatu lengenyili pyuo iso karenge doko
\q1 
\v 4 wamba yangama kopa yake dokona see nalyamopa neta iki rao karenge dopale ingilyamo.
\q1 Dee baa apunda epo sokwa pelyamopa netame isako dupwa leya leya pinyi pyambungi dopale ingilyamo.
\b
\q1 
\v 5 Kamongome namba kando pii kana minyuo lalu lao leya dokona
\q1 Anatumi nambana manjirunu dupwa elyape keta pisinyi pyambwakara.
\q1 Dee pii angi kinyi walengena palyuo yaki nyuo kaeya naro, leya.
\q1 Pii lalu lao lapala alowa pii nange dokona namba moname nyilyamo.
\q1 Dokona Anatumi namba dopa pyuo angi pyakaramo dokopa anamasi minyuo kararo.
\q1 
\v 6 Dopa piramopa akali Anatu suu pyaa nange dupwa nepereke neta nembenge dopale ingyuo nembenge.
\q1 Dokopa wambu mendemepe kingimi minyandara ingya nange.
\q1 
\v 7 Mendeme puu reke karenge doko minyandalena suu pyarami ramo doko bange aneme wasisipi dee kakupi lapo nyepala minyarami.
\q1 Dokopa nepereke puu doko isareme rao otalu oto otara.
\s3 23:8—24:25 Pii lumwa pyuo reteya. Dapitinya yanda singi mupwa dupwana kingi pyasi palamo. Yuu mendepa nakamame Isaraele wambupi Juta wambupi yaka leyaminyi dokona pii palamo. Dee yuu mendepa wambu malu yanyi nyiyaminyipa Kamongo dokome yanyi isa palyiya. Pii dupwa palamo. 
